text:
{
    "tiddlers": {
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n      <$image alt=\"Cover\" style=\"\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/images/OEBPS/1114309976206040498_26748-cover.png\"></$image>\n      \n    </div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>The Project Gutenberg EBook of Huan Zhong You, by Yanxia Zhuren</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>This eBook is for the use of anyone anywhere at no cost and with\nalmost no restrictions whatsoever.  You may copy it, give it away or\nre-use it under the terms of the Project Gutenberg License included\nwith this eBook or online at www.gutenberg.org</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Title: Huan Zhong You</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>Author: Yanxia Zhuren</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>Release Date: October 2, 2008 [EBook #26748]</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>Language: Chinese</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK HUAN ZHONG YOU ***</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Produced by Hui-Ting Chuang</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第一回  老宿儒七貼方登第</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    詩曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    修士讀書認理真，几忘氣化有屈伸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    游魂為變原不昧，漫道人間無鬼神。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說萬歷年間，湖廣黃州府羅田縣，有一個秀才，姓石名峨，字</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>峻峰，別號嵐庵。乃洛陽石洪之后。為無未避亂，流落此處。家有房</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>宅一所，田地數頃。為人素性剛方，不隨時好，不信鬼神。夫人竺氏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>惠而且賢，中饋針織外，黃卷青燈，恆以相夫讀書為務。因此峻峰學</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>業成就。每逢考試，獨冠一軍。四方聞風，無不爭相景仰，樂為結納</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。可惜時運坑坷，隊_功名。凡進六場，不是命題差題，就是文中空</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>白。不是策內忘了抬頭，便是表里漏了年號。一連七次，俱被貼出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>但窮且益堅，立志不懈，待至年過四十，卻又是一個科分。這正是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    肯把工夫用百倍，那怕朱表不點頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    凡大比之年，前數月內，魁星偏（遍）閱各省。揀其學問充足，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>培植深厚者，各照省數勒定一冊，獻于文昌。文昌奏之玉帝，玉帝登</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>之榜上，張諸天門。名曰：天榜。是科，石峨早已列在天榜數內。及</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>至八月秋闈，三場如意而出。回至家中，向夫人竺氏道：“今科三場</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，俱不被貼，吾已中矣！”夫人答道：“相公果能高發，正是合家之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>慶。”到得揭曉，果然獲蒙鄉荐。及來春會試，又捷報南宮。二年之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>間，身登兩榜。只因朝綱不振，權奸當道。立意家居，無心宦途。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    生有一子，表字九畹，取名茂蘭，一名蕙郎。乃武曲星所轉。從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>小丰姿超眾，聰明非凡，甫離襁褓，即通名物。七歲讀書，竟能目視</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>十行，日誦百篇。不過三五年間，把五經左史，諸子百家等書，俱各</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>成誦在胸，熟如弗鼎。開筆作文，落落有大家風味。長至一十五歲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不惟文章工巧，詩賦精通，亦且長于書畫。一縣之人群呼為石家神童</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。峻峰竊喜，以為此子頭角崢嶸，日后必能丕振家聲，光昭祖業。“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>吾何必身列N班，甘于任人進退耶？”不仕之志，因此益堅。明朝定</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>例，凡一科會試榜發，除鼎甲詞林外，其余進士，三年內務要用完。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>因宦官專權，人多畏禍。殿試后，假托事故，家居不出者，十人之中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，不下四五。緣此詮選之時，人材短少，吏部奏道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    朝廷開科取士，原以黼黻皇猷，非使叨膺名器。茲逢選期，人材</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>短少，皆因歷科進士，多甘家居，致有此弊。伏乞聖裁，飭各省巡撫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，查明報部，提京面檢。如或年力精壯，可以備員，即發往各省補缺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。庶人材出，而百職修矣。謹疏奏聞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    疏上，皇上批道：准依奏覽。部文行各省，各省行各府，各府行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>各縣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    一日，石峻峰偶到縣衙吏房。該管書吏一見峻峰，口稱：“石老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>爺來的湊巧，我正要著人去送信。”峻峰道：“有何信送？”書吏道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“今有部文提你赴京檢驗，文是夜日晚上到的，今早發房。若不信</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>時，請到房里一看。”遂讓峻峰房里坐下，把文查出遞與峻峰。峻峰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一見這文，心中不快，閉口無言。書吏又道：“這文提的甚緊，速起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>縣文，上省去請咨，咨文到縣，約得半月有余。家中速打點行裝，咨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>文到時，即便起身。斷勿遲滯，致使再催。”方才說完，這個書吏，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>被傳入宅里去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    峻峰出衙回家，路上度量此事。不覺形諸顏色，到了家中，夫人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>問道：“相公往日，從外而來，甚是歡喜。今日面帶憂容，是何緣故</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>？”峻峰道：“今日適到縣衙，見有部文，提我上京檢驗。意欲不去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，系聖上的旨意。去時倘或驗中，目下群小專權，恐易罹禍網，貽累</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子孫。事在兩難，躊躇不決，故爾如此。”夫人道：“這事有何作難</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，皇上提去驗看，原系隆重人材。相公趁此上京，博得一職，選得一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>縣。上任后，自勵清操，勿蹈貪墨，縱有權奸，其奈你何？做得三年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兩載，急為告退。既不至上負朝廷，又可以下光宗族。兩全之道，似</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>莫過此，這是妾之愚見，不知相公以為何如？”峻峰答道：“夫人言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>之有理，但上京一去，往返須得半載。蕙即年當垂髫，夫人亦系女輩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。家中無人料理，如何叫我放心去得？”夫人道：“這卻無妨，我已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>年近五旬，一切家務，盡可支持。蒼頭趙才，為人忠誠，外邊叫他照</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>料。蕙郎雖幼，我嚴加查考，他也斷不至于放蕩。自管放心前去，無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>須挂懷。”峻峰道：“夫人既是這樣，吾意已決。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    次日就赴縣，起文上省請咨。家中湊對盤費，收拾行囊。一切親</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>友或具帖奉餞，或饋送贐禮。來來往往，倏忽間已是半月。吏房著人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來說：“咨文已經到縣，請石老爺領文起程。”石峻峰領得咨文在手</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，就雇了一只大船名為“杉飛”。帶了一個書童叫做“來喜”。擇日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>起身，又與夫人竺氏，彼此囑托了一番。這才領著蕙郎送至河岸，看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>著峻峰上船入艙。打鑼開船，然后回家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說峻峰這一路北來，順風揚帆。經了些波濤，過了些閘壩。不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>下月余，已到京都。下的船來，才落店時，就有長班投來伺侯。次日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，歇了一天。第三日早晨，長班領著，就親赴吏部衙門，把咨文投訖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。仔細打聽，進京者還無多人。吏部出一牌道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    部堂示諭，應檢進士知悉：俟各省投文齊集日，另行擇期，當堂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>面驗。各人在寓靜候，勿得自誤。特示。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    峻峰見了這牌，店里靜坐無事，除同人拜往外，日逐帶著來喜在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>街上游玩。玉泉山、白塔寺、藥王廟、菜市口，俱各走到。一日，飯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>后出的門來。走到一個胡同里，看見一個說《西游》的，外邊聽的層</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>層圍著。峻峰來到跟前，側耳一聽，卻說的是劉全進瓜，翠蓮還魂一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>回。峻峰自思道：“無稽之談，殊覺厭聽。”往前走去，到了琉璃場</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>前。心中觸道：“這是天師府舊第，昔日天師在京，此地何等熱鬧？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>目今天師歸山，落得這般蒼涼。天運有升沉，人事有盛衰。即此可以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>想見一班。“憑吊了一會，嗟嘆了几聲。遂口詠七言律一首，以舒慨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    景物變遷誠靡常，結廬何須飾雕梁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    阿房雖美宮終焚，銅雀空名台已荒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    舞館歌樓今安在？頹垣碎瓦徒堪傷！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    古來不乏名勝地，難免后人作戰場。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    詩才詠完，回頭看時，路旁一人，手拿舊書一部，插草出賣。要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過來看，乃是《牡丹庭（亭）記》。峻峰想道：“此書是四大傳奇之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一，系湯玉茗所作。我卻未曾看過。店中悶坐無聊，何不買來一看，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>以當消遣。”因問道：“這書你要多少錢？”那人答道：“要錢四百</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>文。”峻峰道：“這書紙板雖好，卻不甚新鮮了。從來殘物不過半價</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，給你二百錢罷。”那人道：“還求太爺高升。”峻峰喜其說話吉利</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，便道：“既要看書，何得惜錢。”叫來喜接過書來，付與他錢二百</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>五十文。那人得錢欣然而去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    峻峰回到店中，吃了晚飯。叫來喜點起燭來，把這書放在桌上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>從頭看起，初看《驚夢離魂》以及《冥判》諸出，見其曲詞雅倩，集</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>唐工穩，幽思奧想，別有洞天。極口稱道：“玉茗公真才人也！”及</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>看到《開墓還魂》一出，鼓掌大笑道：“人氣聚則生，氣散則死。死</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生者人之所必不免也。死而復生，那有此理？”伯有作歷，申生見巫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，韓退之猶以為左氏浮夸，無足取信。湯玉茗才學名世，何故造此誕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>漫不經之語，惶惑后人也。疑鬼疑神，學人大病。家有讀書子弟，切</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不可令見此書，以蕩其心。”遂叫來喜就燭上一火焚之。峻峰在京候</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>驗不題。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但未知蕙郎與夫人在家如何？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第二回  幼神童一相定終身</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說蕙郎在家，自他父親上京去后，逐日不離書房，功夫愈加純</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>正。母親竺氏亦時常查考，凡平日讀過的書籍，從新溫了一遍。每逢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>三八會期，求他母親命題一道，作文一篇。非迎送賓客，足跡并不到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>大門。如是者，兩月有余。一日，偶到門前，見街上走路的，這個說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>呂公在世，那個說陳摶復生。唧唧噥噥，三五成群，一直往東去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>蕙郎問趙才道：“這是為何？互相稱獎。”趙才答道：“十字街口東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，有個相面先生，說他系云南大理府人，姓曹名奇，道號通玄子。一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>名曹半仙。他的相法，是從天台山得來的。相的委實與眾不同，因此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>哄動了一城人。大相公何不也去相相呢！”蕙郎道：“我去是要去，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>倘或太太找我，你說上對門王相公家講書去了。”趙才應道：“曉得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    蕙郎出了大門，往東直走。又轉過兩道小巷，抬頭一看，已是寓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>首了。但見口東路北，一簇人圍著個相士。里三層，外三層，擁擠不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>動。蕙郎到了跟前，并不能鑽入人空里去，只得在外邊靜聽。聞其指</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>示詳細，評斷決絕，心中已暗暗稱奇。適值相士出來小解，看見蕙郎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>便驚道：“相公也是來相面的嗎？”蕙郎答道：“正是。”相士道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“好個出奇的貴相！”蕙郎道：“小生陋貌俗態，有何奇貴？先生莫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>非過獎了。”相士道：“良驥空群，自應詫目，豈是過獎。相公真要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>相時，今日天色已晚，一時相不仔細。明日飯后，在敝寓專等，肯賜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>光否？”蕙郎道：“既是如此，明日定來請教。但不知先生寓在何處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>？”相士道：“從這條街上東去，見一個小胡同，往北直走，走到盡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>北頭，向東一拐，又是一條東西街，名為賢孝坊。從西頭往東數，路</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>北第五家，就是敝寓。門口有招牌可認。”蕙郎道：“我明日定去領</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>教，但恐先生不在家，被人請去。”相士道：“一言約定，決不相欺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”蕙郎作別而去。相士也收拾了壇場，去回寓所。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說蕙郎回到家中，步進書房。適趙才送茶到此，蕙郎問道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>太太曾找我么？”趙才答道：“不曾。請問大相公，曾叫他相過否？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”蕙郎道：“這人真正相的好，但今日時候迫促，相不仔細，說定明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日在下處等我。我稟知太太，明日飯后，一定要去的。”蕙郎把相面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一事擱在心頭，通夜并沒睡著。次早起來，向母親竺氏道：“今日天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>氣晴明，孩兒久困書房，甚是疲倦，意欲出去走走。街上有個相士，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>相的出奇，還要求他給相相。孩兒不敢擅去，特來稟知母親。”夫人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“這我卻不禁止，你但出去，務要早回，我才放心。”蕙郎答道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“孩兒也不敢在外久住，毋煩母親囑咐。”用過早飯，封了五錢銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子，藏在袖內。并不跟人，出門徑往賢孝坊去了。蕙郎一來，這正是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    展開奇書觀異相，鼓動鐵舌斷英才。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    蕙郎到了這街西頭，向東一望，路北第五家門口，果然有個招牌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，上寫“通玄子寓處”五字。蕙郎走到門前，叫道：“曹先生在家么</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>？”內有一小廝應道：“現在。”蕙郎走進大門。往西一拐，又有個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>朝南的小門。進了這門，迎門是一池竹子。竹子旁邊，有兩株老梅，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>前面放著許多的花盆。轉過池北是三間堂房，前出一廈，甚是干淨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>往里一看，后檐上放著一張條桌，上面擺著三事。前邊八仙桌一張，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>擱著几本相書，放著文房四寶。牆上挂一橫匾，寫道：“法宗希夷”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>四字。旁邊貼一對聯，上寫道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    心頭有鑒斷明天下休咎事，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    眼底無花觀遍域中往來人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    蕙郎正在打量，小廝進去說道：“有客來訪。”那相士連忙走出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>相迎，道：“相公真不失信，老夫久候多時了。”讓到屋里，分賓主</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>坐下。叫小廝潑了一壺好茶來，彼此對飲了几杯。相士開言道：“算</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>卦相面，先打聽了人家的虛實，然后再為相算，名曰‘買春’。這是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>江湖中人的衣缽，予生平誓不為此。相公的尊姓大名，并系何等人家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，暫且不問。俟相過后，再請教罷。”蕙郎道：“如此說先生的大號</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，小生也不便請問了。”相士道：“相公的貴相，非一言半語，可以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>說完，請到里邊相看，尤覺僻靜。”相士領著蕙郎，從東間后檐上一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個小門進去。又是朝西的兩間豎頭屋。前檐上盡是亮窗，窗下放著一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>張四仙小桌，對放著兩把椅子。北山上鋪著一張藤床，床上放著鋪蓋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。后檐上挂著一軸古畫，乃張子房杞橋進履圖。兩邊放著兩張月牙小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>桌，這桌上擱著雙陸圍棋，那桌上放著羌苗牙板。蕙郎稱贊道：“先</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生如此擺設，真清雅人也。”相士答道：“旅邸草茅，未免污目。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    兩個對面坐定，相士把蕙郎上下細看了一番。說道：“相公的貴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>相，天庭高聳，地閣方圓。兩顴特立，准頭丰隆。真五岳朝天之相，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日后位至三公，自不必說。但印堂上微有厄氣，天根亦微涉斷缺，恐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不利于少年。相書有云：一八、十八、二十八，下至眉攢上至發，是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>為上部，主少年。自天根至鼻頭，是為中部，主中年。自承漿至頦下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，是為下部，主末年。貴相自十八至二十八，這十年未免有些坑坷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過得二十八歲漸入佳境。到得五十六十，功在廟社，名垂竹帛，顯貴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>極矣，以后不必再相了。”蕙郎道：“先生如此過獎，小生安敢望此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”相士道：“我言不妄發，日后定驗。”蕙郎又問道：“先生既精</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>相法，亦通柱理嗎？”相士道“相法按八卦，分九宮。命理講格局，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>論官祿。其實陰陽五行，生克制化，一而二，二而一者也。”蕙郎道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“如此說來，先生不惟會相，亦且會算了，愿把賤造，再煩先生一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>看。總為致謝，未知先生肯否？”相士道：“這卻使得。”蕙郎就將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>八字寫出，相士接過來看了看說道：“貴造刑沖不犯，官殺清楚，誠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>貴人格也。是九歲順行運，自九歲至十九，還在父母運內，無容多說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。細看流年，不出月余，定有喜事臨門。自十九至二十九，這十年大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>運不通，子平說的好：‘老怕長生少怕衰，中年只怕病與胎。’你這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>十年行的正是胎運。過此以后，官星得權，百事如意了。但年年細查</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，不勝推算。待我總批几句，親身領會罷。遂提筆寫讖語八句云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    學堂星動繼紅鸞，何料喪門忽到前。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    驛馬能牽大耗至，陰伏天牢緊相纏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    幸逢武曲照當命，那怕傷宮與比肩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    壽星應主晚歲運，一生福祿自延綿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    寫完遞與蕙郎說道：“相公，你一生的遭際，盡在八句話中。挨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>次經去，半點不錯。此帖務要收好，勿致遺失。”遂拱手說道：“語</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>少忌諱，萬望包涵。”蕙郎謝道：“代為指迷曷勝感佩。”就把謝禮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>呈上，相士道：“老夫半生江湖，只重義氣，不計錢財。相公日后高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>發，定有相逢之處。何必拘在一時，厚儀斷不敢領。”蕙郎再三相讓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，相士極力推辭。蕙郎見其出于誠心，說道：“先生既然不肯，小生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>另當致敬。尊命安好過違。”遂把封套袖起，相士方才問道：“相公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>尊姓大名呢？”蕙郎答道：“小生姓石名茂蘭，賤字九畹。住在永寧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>街上，家君諱峨，字是峻峰。系壬午舉人，癸未進士。現今赴京候檢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，去有兩個多月了。相士道：“既然尊翁大人赴京檢驗，不出月余，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>定有喜信。這一句已是應驗了。”彼此又盤桓了一會，蕙郎告辭，再</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>三的致謝。相士送至門外，彼此作別而去。卻說這個相士住了些時，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不知流落何方。街上再不見他相面了。蕙郎在家不題。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但未知峻峰在京候驗如何？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第三回  念民艱挂冠歸故里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石峻峰在京候驗，住至月余，并無音信。一日，長班走來稟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“小的今早經過吏部門前，見有牌示了。限于初四日早刻齊集，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>當堂面驗。今日初三，就是明晨了。老爺把靴帽衣服，逐一打整停當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。小的明日早來，好跟老爺同去。或坐車，或坐轎，今日雇下，省的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>明晨忙迫。”峻峰稱了三錢銀子，著長班去雇車子，就把衣帽等物，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>逐一檢點了一番。叫來喜俱各包妥。用過午飯，轉瞬天黑。峻峰早早</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>關門睡去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    次早起來，叫來喜要水洗了臉，梳了頭，用過了早飯。店主方才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去開店門，長班進來稟道：“車子已到，請老爺早去，勿致有誤。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>就把衣包、帽盒，送在車上。峻峰上車坐定，長班卻先走了。車夫使</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>著車子，來喜隨后跟著。霎時間，已到吏部門首。長班前來稟道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>路北有一個茶館，甚是清雅。老爺下車，暫歇片時，換了衣服，再上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>衙門。”峻峰下的車來，見路北門面鋪上，挂著“煮茗齋”三字一個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>小招牌。進到里面，是三間瓦廈。兩邊俱是開窗。中間門上吊著帘子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，院內東西兩邊，俱是走廊。時當九月，東廊下放著几盆金菊。西廊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>下挂著兩籠畫眉。峻峰步入房中，見后檐上貼著“聊勝指梅”四字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>下邊貼“茶賦”一篇云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    惟龍團之津液，與雀舌之汁膏。解睡余之煩渴，醒酒后之號呶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>爾乃黃芽披蒸，綠腳垂潔。碧乳翻濤，銀絲勝雪。列三等以為差，冠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>六□而獨□。酩可為奴，筵堪伴果。味品香泉，烹須爐火。盛玉罌其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>常湛，轉金碾以成垛。至若經作陸羽，錄著蔡襄。添溫暖于冬腹，滌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>炎熱于夏腸。既無恤夫冰卮，又何羨乎瓊漿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    兩旁又貼一對聯云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    開戶迎花笑，啟窗聽鳥鳴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    峻峰里面坐了一會，換過衣服。長班來稟道：“大人將近升堂，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>請老爺過衙門去罷。”峻峰跟著長班，走到儀門前邊，挨省次站定。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>大人已上堂，從北直驗起。一省或驗中二十多人，或驗中十五六人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>點到峻峰，吏部停筆問道：“你原籍何處？”峻峰應道：“原籍河南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，后遷湖廣。”吏部又問道：“洛陽石浚川先生，是你一脈嗎？”峻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>峰應道：“是進士的上世先祖。傳至于今，已二十二代了。”吏部笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“你既系先儒苗裔，又當年力精壯，正該為朝廷出力報效。奈何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>追蒿邙之高風，負王家之遴選。你且下去，明日再聽發落。”并未說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>驗中與沒驗中。峻峰下的堂來，心中甚是恍惚，不敢就走。直候到各</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>省驗完，大人退堂，方才回寓。心中度量了一夜。到得次早，叫長班</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去打聽，回來稟道：“小的見吏部書辦說：大人已經啟奏，再看旨下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>如何？”峻峰心中愈加驚慌，住了兩天，親去打聽。吏部已把聖諭貼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    奉天承運皇帝詔曰：朕思賢為國寶，安可野有留良。茲依部奏，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>驗中進士，二百八十人。大省二十名，中省十五名，小省十名，各照</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>數發往候缺。惟石峨系先儒后裔，理應速用，即授陝西西安府長安縣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>知縣。赴部領憑，毋得遲緩。欽此。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    峻峰見了這道旨意，不勝歡喜。領過憑文，請了兩位幕賓，招了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>几名長隨。離了京城，自通州壩上船，星夜往黃州府進發。京報已早</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>到家中，夫人竺氏叫趙才打掃客舍，制辦羊酒，候峻峰來到，以便待</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>客。住了些時，峻峰已到家中，親戚朋友來叩喜者繩繩不絕。熱鬧了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>半月有余。峻峰恐誤了憑限，祭過祖墳，擇一吉日，率領家眾，直往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>長安上任去了。這正是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    雪里無人來送炭，錦上誰不去添花。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說峻峰一入陝西境界，就有人役來接。峻峰略把土俗民情，問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了一番。因問“衙門廣狹怎樣？”來役稟道：“官衙內有鬼，歷來的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>老爺，俱住民宅。小的來時，早已雇賃停當，修理齊楚。無煩老爺再</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>為經心。”峻峰笑道：“本縣素性是不怕鬼的。我定住官衙，不進民</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>舍。你等作速回去，給我收拾官衙，違者到任重責。”來役跪央再三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，決于不准。只得星夜趕回，把官衙打掃出來。峻峰一到縣時，直就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>官衙內上任。是晚，更夫巡夜，聞有鬼說道：“石青天在此居官，吾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>等暫且回避。”從此官衙內，安靜無事了。上任三日，行香放告已畢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。查前任的案卷，未結者還有二三十件，或出票，或出簽，把一干人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>犯，俱各拘齊。出一牌示：“本縣擬于某日，升堂理事。滿城士民，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>愿看者概為不禁。”到得那日清晨，衙門里人就填滿了。峻峰自飯后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>升堂，坐至日夕。二三十件案卷，俱經理清。當批者批，當斷者斷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>該打的打，該罰的罰。無不情真罪當。一時看者，群驚為神。峻峰把</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>眾人喚到案前，曉諭道：“本縣承乏茲土，雖無龐士龍之材，卻有西</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>門豹之心。在此居官一日，必不使爾等坐受阽危也。”眾人叩謝而散</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。歷任一年，政簡刑清。做至三年，頌聲載道。城內紳衿鄉間百姓，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>送萬民衣的，送萬民傘的。貼德政歌的，紛紛不一。峻峰悉行阻卻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>特出一告條云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    長吏為民父母，兆民皆吾子也。父母育子不聞居功，長吏恤民豈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>意望報。嗣后媚諛之事，斷不可復。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    一縣之人無可圖報，遂題詩刻石，以銘其德云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    愛民勿徒羨巽黃，竊幸邑侯稱循良。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    繭績不繇咸淳化，嗚琴堪并單父堂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    割雞聊把牛刀試，買犢旋慶筑麥場。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    頂祝焚香情莫盡，永登貞鈱志不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    后天啟皇帝登基，太監魏忠賢專權用事。峻峰急欲退去，告優未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>暇，忽越級升了廣西柳州府知府。到任三月怡化翔洽，適廣西巡撫提</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>進省議事。峻峰星夜赴省，來見憲台。巡撫道：“傳貴府來，非商別</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>事，今有東廠魏大人發下銀子三十萬。叫本院散給各府，各府散給各</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>縣，放于民間使用，三分起息，然后本利催齊解司。下歲領去再放。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>貴府該代放銀六萬兩。作速領去，分派州縣。”峻峰稟道：“大人之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>命，卑職固不敢違，但柳州府地瘠民貧，兼之連歲凶歉。有者典當田</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>宅，無者鬻賣妻子。自顧不贍，那有余錢，代為出息。還求大人極力</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>挽轉，務使百姓均沾實惠。”巡撫道：“這是東廠大人的鈞旨，誰敢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>抗違。”峻峰跪央道：“百姓是朝廷的百姓，官員是朝廷的官員。朝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>廷設官，原為牧民。并非設官代人放賬。卑職只上知有皇上，下知有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>百姓，中知有大人。若浚民生而肥內監，這等樣事卑職斷不敢做，亦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不肯做。還求大人三思。”巡撫道：“如此說，難道你不顧你的考成</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>嗎？”峻峰起來冷笑道：“吾人出仕，原以行節，非圖固寵。卑職自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>幼讀書，頗有志氣。昔陶淵明不為五斗米折腰，吾寧為五馬榮挫志乎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>？大人既不肯為萬民作主，卑職斷不給太監放債。”巡撫怒道：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這等的抗上，本院一定題參。”峻峰答道：“與其待大人題參，何如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>卑職先自引退。”遂告辭而出，銀子分文不領。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    回到署中，把倉庫檢點了一番，并無半點虧欠。未結的案卷逐一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>理清，應發的發回本縣。把他的印綬，親身送到巡撫衙門。撫院一見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，甚是不悅。峻峰稟道：“百姓不可一日無官。居官不可一時無印。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>卑職既得罪東廠大人，豈容卑職久留此地。望大人暫且把印收去，以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>便委人。如魏大人加以罪譴，就是焚尸滅族，卑職愿以身當。并不累</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>大人。”說到此處，那巡撫就把印收去了。峻峰從省回衙，掩門待罪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。住有半月，并無風信。遂雇了車轎，率領家屬，仍回黃州去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    不知峻峰回去如何？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>         第四回  為友誼捐資置新宅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說石峻峰棄官回署。巡撫委官盤查倉庫，無半點虧欠，案卷無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一件停留。只得一面委人看署，一面修書報與京中。書道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    叩稟：東廠司理監，魏大人座下。前承大人發下銀兩，卑職徑定</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>府縣俱各派去。獨柳州府知府石峨抗違不領，兼以棄官脫逃。特為稟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>明，以便究治。專候鈞旨，肅此上達。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    廣西巡撫某人頓首</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    魏忠賢拆書一看，心中想道：“放賬滾利，終屬私事。且石峨為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人剛直，十分究治，未必甘罪。倘或皇上聞知更覺不妥。莫若將機就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>機，叫他去罷。”遂寫一回書道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    茲承來札，俱已心照。柳州府知府石峨，雖系抗上，乃皇上親放</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>之人，不便究處。且素稱廉明，□□民望，棄官回籍，聽其引退。勿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>得從刻，照書施行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    某月某日東廠特發</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石峻峰轉升之后，巡撫上疏，另題補了長安縣一員知縣。姓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>王名o字止珍，乃廣東廣州府番禺縣人。系進士出身。往長安上任，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>路過襄陽府。襄陽府城內，有一個致仕的員外，姓胡名水榮字涵齋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>與王o素系年誼。王o來到襄陽拜看胡水榮。胡水榮設席邀請。席間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，王o向胡員外道：“小弟先去上任，少停半載，再接賤眷。自番禺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>直抵長安，路徑太長，一氣難以打到。弟欲向年兄借一閑房，在此作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個過棧。兩截走，庶不艱苦。不知年兄肯相幫否？”胡員外答道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>寶眷到此，小弟理應照料，那煩年兄啟口。”王o道：“既蒙年兄慨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>許，小弟就謝過了。”席終之后，王o回店，次日起身走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說胡員外又自想道：“凡官員的家眷，少則二三十口，多則四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>五十人。現在住的宅子，終是安置不下，且不便宜。莫若另買一宅，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>權叫他住。一則全了朋友之誼，二則添些家產，豈不兩全。”算計已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>定，遂叫官中，代為買房。本街西頭路南，有房子一處。房主姓徐名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>敦，本因宅子里有鬼，住不安穩。要賣了另置。就出了一張五百兩銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子的文約，交給官中楊小山。楊小山因向胡家來說，胡員外問道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這房子他實在要多少銀子？”楊小山道：“依他說要銀五百兩。”胡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>員外給他三百五十兩。說來說去，講到四百五十兩，徐家就應口賣了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。胡員外擇了日期，同著親朋，叫楊小山寫了文約，把價銀足數兌去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。徐家把宅子騰出，交給胡員外。他另搬到別處去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說王o到任，住了半年。寫了一封家書，差了一個的當家人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>往廣東去接家眷。家中男女，上下共有二十余人。一路直投襄陽府胡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>宅而來。胡員外著人把新買的宅子，打掃潔淨。請王夫人與公子住在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里面。一切照料，無不盡心。歇近一月，正要起身而去。忽有一個家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人，星夜趕來。稟道：“老爺已于四月間病故，小的料太太少爺，還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>在此處。特來報知，好去搬靈。”夫人公子聽說，哭倒在地，半日方</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>蘇。公子與夫人計議，此處到長安尚有兩千余里。往來盤費，非同些</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>小，手中無錢，如何去的。夫人道：“央你胡年伯，或者相幫，也未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>可定。”王公子親到胡員外家里，央他幫些銀子，去接父靈。胡員外</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>慨許，借銀二百兩。王公子得了銀子，領著一個家人，往長安縣搬靈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去了。往返四五個月，才把靈柩搬到襄陽府來。胡員外城外有一處小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>房，叫他把靈柩停在里邊。胡員外辦禮制帳，親去祭奠。其祭文云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    維吾兄之才略兮，堪稱國良。甫操刀于小邑兮，治具畢張。苟驥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>足之大展兮，化被無方。胡皇天其不佑兮，遽夢黃梁。悲哲人之已萎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兮，我心傍徨。陳壤奠于靈前兮，鑒茲薄觴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    這且按下不題。卻說廣東士寇大發，把廣州一帶俱被占去。王知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>縣的靈柩一時難以回家。夫人公子，只得在此久住。住有一年，夜間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>漸聞鬼聲，且見鬼形。夫人公子總不肯說出，恐負了胡員外的好意。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>又住了几月，王夫人并上下人等，俱病死宅中。只剩得王公子夫婦二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人，與他庶母所生的一個妹子，年方十一二歲。后廣東賊冠平息，胡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>員外又助銀百有余兩，叫王公子押著他父母的靈柩，轉回廣東去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>落下這處閑房，并沒人敢在里邊去住。胡員外托官中典賣。俱嫌宅子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不吉，總無售主。只得把大門常常鎖著。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    忽一夜間，胡員外夢見一個老叟，蒼顏白發，手執藜杖，登門來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了。說道：“小弟姓焦名寧馨。系紹興府人氏，有一件要事相懇。西</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>頭路南宅子內有我一親女、一甥女并一甥男。住已數年，今聞尊兄要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>賣此宅，但這兩個女子，與尊兄有父子之分。日后就這宅子上還要招</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一佳婿，以光門婿。切不可妄聽人言，輕為拋舍。”胡員外醒來，把</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>夢中的言語告訴夫人馮氏。馮氏夫人道：“夢寐之事，何足為憑。依</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>我看來，咱家盡有錢使，何必典賣房宅，惹人恥笑。與其不值半文舍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>給人家。何如從新拆蓋，賃出打租。”胡員外道：“夫人說得極是。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>我從今再不賣他了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到得次夜，時近三更，胡夫人有□未睡。忽見兩個女子，丰姿綽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>約，顏色俏麗。領著一個六七歲的小兒，□□緩步從外而來。見了胡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>夫人，深深一拜。一齊就跪下磕頭。胡夫人兩手扶起問道：“兩位姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>姐，你是何人？為何行這樣大禮。老身斷不敢當。”二女子道：“兒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>等住在西頭宅子上，已經几年。今因王夫人上下死在里面。義父說宅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子凶惡住不的了，屢次托人變賣。幸得母親一言勸醒就不賣了。兒等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>能得安居此處，以待良緣。為此特來相謝。”說罷飄然而去。胡夫人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>甚是駭異，叫醒胡員外。把見兩女子的事，說與他聽。胡員外道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>夫人所見與吾夢相符。此中必有緣故。這宅子我定是不賣了。但不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>后來，應在何處？”這正是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    有緣千里來相會，無緣對面不相逢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    且按下不提。卻說這宅子對門，有一個孝廉公姓朱名耀彩，字斐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>文。年近五旬，他發身時，是中的解元。會試曾荐元三次，俱未得中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。閩省之人，群稱為文章宗匠，理學名宿。他有一個兒子，名■，字</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>良玉。年方二十三歲，是個食廩的生員。人物聰俊，學問充足。王公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子在此住時，門首時常相見。王公子羨慕朱■。朱■也欽仰王公子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>王公子也是個補了廩的秀才，因是同道朋友，兩個就拜成兄弟。王夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人與朱■的母親，亦時相往來，彼此情意甚覺投合。王夫人的女兒并</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>拜朱夫人為義母。王夫人在日，朱夫人不時的把王小姐接過這院修理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>頭面，添補衣裳，待之無異親生。及王夫人夫婦靈柩歸家有期，朱夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人又把王小姐接過來，照料了一番。說道：“吾兒我與你果有緣法，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日后須落在一塊方好。但你居廣東，我住湖廣，云山間阻，從此一別</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，今生斷不能再見面了。”說罷，不覺泣下。王小姐答道：“孩兒仗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>托母親的福力，安知后日不常靠著母親。”亦自滴淚滿懷。從此王夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人夫婦靈柩回去。朱夫人日逐想念王小姐，几乎成病。數月以后，方</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>才開懷。王小姐回到家中，父母大事已過。兄嫂欲為他擇配，王小姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>也不便當面阻絕。作詩一首，貼于房中。其詩云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    婚姻大事系前緣，媒氏冰人徒枉然。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    義母臨岐曾有約，常思歸落在伊邊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    年過二十方許嫁，且托繡閨讀史篇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    若使赤繩強相系，情甘一命赴黃泉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    自從王小姐作詩之后，擇配一事，兄嫂二人，也再不敢提了。卻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>說番禺縣有一個極靈驗的巫婆，能知人已往將來的事情。一日，走到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>王宅看見王小姐說道：“這個姑娘，定是一位夫人。但必須經過三個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>娘家，方才成人。可惜形神之間，將來不無變換，這是數該如此，也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不是他好意這般。”王夫人仔細相問，那巫婆答道：“事系渺冥，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>可說破，到了那時，便自明白。”又待問時，那巫婆撤身而出。王夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人把這話告訴王公子，王公子道：“巫婆之言，殊屬可惡。”從此分</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>付看門的：“一切巫婆人等，俱不准進門。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    王小姐自見那巫婆之后，漸漸的懶于見人。日逐在他臥樓上，做</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>些針指，并不輕發言笑。長至一十五歲時，容顏甚是標致。忽然坐了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一個病根，一時昏去，半日方醒。王公子延醫調治，總不見痊。王公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子怨他夫人叫巫婆進院，所以致的他妹子這樣。王小姐聞知勸說道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“人生在世，死生有命。一個巫婆，他如何就能勾叫我這樣，哥哥斷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不可瞞怨嫂子。”王公子聽說，方才緘口。且休說王小姐后日怎樣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    尚未知石峻峰回來如何，再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第五回  孝順男變產還父債</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石峻峰回得家來，關門避事。自與蕙郎講几篇文章，論几章</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>經史。除此以外，晴明天氣，約相契三四人，閑出郊外，臨流登山，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>酌酒賦詩而已。那蕙郎未有妻室，與未入泮宮，是他留心的兩件要事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。一日，在客舍內靜坐。見兩個媒婆先到面前，一個叫做周大腳，一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個叫做馬長腿。笑著說道：“幸逢老爺在家，俺兩個方不枉費了腳步</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”峻峰問道：“你兩個是為大相公的婚事而來嗎？”二媒婆答道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“正是為此而來。”峻峰道：“你兩個先到里面，向太太說知，我隨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>后就到。”二媒婆聽說，走入中堂去了。石夫人一見說道：“你兩個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>老媒，為何久不來俺家走走？”二媒婆答道：“俺不是給大相公揀了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一頭好親事，還不得閑上太太家來哩。”石夫人問道：“是說的那一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家？”二媒婆答道：“是十字街南，路東房老爺家。他家的小姐今年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>十八，姿色十分出眾。工針指，通文墨。房太太只這一位小姐，還有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一付好陪送哩。太太與老爺商量，若是中意，俺兩個好上那頭去說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”夫人道：“這卻也好。”叫來喜：“去請老爺進來。”峻峰進得房</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>中，坐下。夫人向著說道：“兩個老媒為蕙郎議親，說的是房家，在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>十字口南邊住。你可知道么？”峻峰道：“這是做太河衛守備的房應</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>魁。”二媒答道：“正是，正是。”峻峰道：“這是無庸打聽的，那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里的姑娘多大小了？”二媒道：“十八歲，人材針指，無一不好，且</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是識文解字。過門時，又有好陪送。說的俱是實話，并不敢半點欺瞞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。老爺，若說是好，俺就向那邊說去。”峻峰道：“別無可說，你房</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>老爺若不嫌我窮時，我就與他結親。”兩媒婆見峻峰夫婦已是應許，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>起身就走。石夫人道：“老媒別走，吃過午飯去。”二媒笑道：“太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>太，常言說的好，熱媒熱媒，不可遲回。俺那頭說妥了，磕頭時一總</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>擾太太罷。”說畢，就出了大門，直往十字口南去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    二媒婆到得房宅，正值房應魁與夫人劉氏小姐翠容，在中堂坐著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>說話。房太太一見，便問道：“你兩個是來給小姐題媒的嗎？”二媒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>應道：“太太倒猜的准。”翠容聽說，把臉紅了紅，頭也不抬，就躲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>在別房里去了。房應魁問道：“說的是那一家？”二媒答道：“永寧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>街上住的石太爺家。”房應魁道：“這是石峻峰，他不給魏太監放賬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，連知府也不做了，好一個硬氣人。他的學生，我曾見過。人物甚好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，學問極通，人俱說他是個神童。目下，卻還未曾進學哩。門當戶對</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，這是頭好親事，說去罷了。”房夫人道：“既是他家，我也曉得。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>但他家土地不多，居官未久，無甚積蓄。恐過門后，日子艱窘。”房</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>應魁道：“人家作親，會揀的揀兒郎，不會揀的揀宅房。貧富自有命</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>定，何必只看眼前。”夫人道：“主意你拿，妾亦不敢過謬。”二媒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>又追問一句道：“老爺太太若是應承，俺兩個明日就磕喜頭了。”房</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>應魁道：“這是何事，既然應允，豈肯更口。”二媒聽說辭出。遲了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兩日，兩媒先到石家磕喜頭，每人賞銀二兩。后到房家磕喜頭，也照</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>數賞銀二兩。石峻峰看了日期換過庚帖，議定臘月十八日過門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    峻峰的要緊心事，就割去一半了。只蕙郎未曾進學，還時刻在念</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。到得六月半間，學院行文歲考。黃州定于七月初二日調齊，初八日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>下馬。峻峰聞信，就打點盤纏，領著蕙郎赴府應考。這個學院最認的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>文章，又喜好書寫。蕙郎進得場時，頭一道題，是季路問事鬼神。次</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>題是，莫非命也。蕙郎下筆如神，未過午刻，兩篇文章，真草俱就。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>略等了一會，學院升堂，蕙郎就把卷子交去。學院見他人才秀雅，送</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>卷神速。遂叫到公案桌前，把卷子展開一看。真個是字字珠璣，句句</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>錦繡。兼之書寫端楷。夸獎道：“此誠翰院材也。”遂拈筆題詩一首</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>以贈之。其詩云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    人材非易得，川岳自降神。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    文體追西漢，筆鋒傲晉人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    箕裘千載舊，經濟一時新。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    養就從龍器，應為王家賓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    蕙郎出得場來，把文章寫給他父親一看。峻峰道：“文章雖不甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>好，卻還有些指望。”及至拆號，蕙郎進了案首。對門王詮進了第二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。卻說王詮乃刑部主事王有章之子，為人甚不端方。兄弟三個，他系</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>居長。自他父母去世，持其家資殷厚，往往暗地里圖謀人家的妻女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>外面總不露像。蕙郎窺看雖透，因是同進，遂成莫逆之交。這且不說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，卻說峻峰領著蕙郎回到家來，不覺已□就是十月盡間。蕙郎的婚期</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>漸近。峻峰打點首飾，制辦衣裳。到了臘月十八的吉期，鼓樂喧天，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>燭火照地。把新人房翠容娶進門來。拜堂已畢，送入洞房。到晚客散</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，夫妻恩愛，自不消說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    過得一月有余，王詮在這邊與蕙郎說話，適值翠容從娘家回來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>偷眼瞧見王詮，問丫頭道：“那是何人？”丫頭答道：“是對門王相</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>公。”翠容默然無言。及到晚間，蕙郎歸房。翠容道：“對門王生，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>獐頭鼠目。心朮定屬不端。常相交接，恐為所害。相公千萬留心方妥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”蕙郎答道：“同學朋友，何必相猜。”翠容因娶的未久，亦不便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>再說了。到得科考，蕙郎蒙取一等一名，補了廩餼，王詮蒙取二等，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>亦成增廣。兩個合伴上省應試。蕙郎二場被貼而回。是歲蕙郎年正十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>九，回想相士所批學堂紅鸞一句，已經應驗。再想喪門到前一句，心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>上卻甚是有些躊躇。及至到了來春三四月間，羅田縣瘟疫大行。峻峰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>夫婦二人，俱染時症相繼而亡。才知相士之言，無一不驗。蕙郎克盡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子道，衣衾棺槨，無不盡心。把父母發送入土。且按下不題。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說魏太監一時雖寬過了石峨，心下終是懷恨。此時西安府，新</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>選了一個知府，姓范名承顏。最好奔走權貴。掣簽后，托人情使銀子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，認在魏太監的門下。一日，特來參見，說話之間，魏太監道及石峨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不給放賬一事。意味之間，甚覺憾然。范承顏答道：“這有何難，卑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>職此去定為大人雪恥。”說定告辭而退。及至范承顏到了任所，留心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>搜尋石峨在任的事件。他居官三年，并無半點不好的事情。惟長安縣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有引河一道，系石峨的前任奉旨所開。數年以來，將近淤平。范承顏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>就以此為由，稟報督撫。說此河雖系石峨前任所開，石峨在任，并不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>疏挑，致使淤平。貽水患害民。理應提回原任，罰銀五千兩，以使賠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>修。撫院具了題，就著西安府行文用印。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石茂蘭在家，那一日是他父親的周年。一切親友都來祭奠，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>午間正有客時。忽然兩個差人，一個執簽，一個提鎖，來到石家門首</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。厲聲叫道：“石相公在家么？”趙才聽說應道：“在家。”石茂蘭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>也隨后跟出來。差人一見，不用分說，就走近前來，把鎖子給石生帶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>上。石生不知何故，大家喧嚷。眾客聽說一齊出來勸解。那差人道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“他是犯了欽差大事，俺們也不敢作主。叫他自己當堂分辨去罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>翠容在內宅，聽說丈夫被鎖。也跑出門外觀望，誰知早被對門王詮看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了盡情。眾人勸解差人不下，也各自散了。翠容見他丈夫事不結局，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>就回到院內哭去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    差人帶著石生，見了縣主。縣主問道：“你就是原任長安縣知縣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石峨的兒子嗎？”石茂蘭答道：“生員正是。”縣主道：“你父親失</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>誤欽工，理應該你賠修。你作速湊辦銀兩，以便解你前去。”石茂蘭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>回道：“此河生父并未經手，賠修應在前任。還求老爺原情。”縣公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“你勿得強辯。著原差押下去，限你一月為期，如或抗違遲誤，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>定行詳革治罪。”石茂蘭滿心被屈，無可奈何。下得堂來，出了衙門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。左右打算，沒處弄錢。只得去找官中，把房宅地土，盡行出約變賣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。這官中拿著文約，各處覓主。此時人人聞知石生之事，恐有連累，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>并沒人敢要。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一日，官中在街上恰恰遇著王詮，提及石茂蘭變產一事。王詮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>心里欲暗圖房翠容，遂說道：“朋友有難，理應相幫，這房宅地土，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>別人不敢要時，我卻暫且留下。俟石兄發財時，任他回贖。但不知文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>約上是要多少銀子？”官中道：“是要四千五百兩。”王詮道：“我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>也并不灠ョA就照數給他。”官中聽了，喜道：“王相公這就是為朋</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>友了。”遂把石茂蘭請到他家，同著差人，官中把正數四千五百兩銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子兌訖。王詮又說道：“我聽說來文是罰銀五千。四千五百兩，長兄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>斷不能了結此。莫如外助銀五百兩，系弟的薄心。”石茂蘭謝道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>感長兄盛情，弟何以報。”就把這五百銀子，也拿在家來了。翠容聞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>知便說道：“對門王家，只可受他的價銀，是咱所應得的。外銀五百</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，未必不有別意，斷不可受。”石茂蘭不聽，把翠容送在娘家去。趙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>才來喜俱各打發走了。遂把宅子地土，一一交清。縣公辦了一道文書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，上寫道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    羅田縣正堂加三級錢，為關移事。敝縣查得，原任長安縣知縣石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>峨，已經身故。票拘伊子石茂蘭。并賠修銀兩五千正。差解投送，貴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>府務取收管，須至移者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    羅田縣差了兩個人役，把石生并銀子直解到西安府去了。石生一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去莫提。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知翠容在家如何？且看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>         第六回  貞烈女舍身報母仇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說房翠容回到娘家，一則挂念石生，又掂度著王家五百兩空銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子。日夜憂愁，容顏漸覺憔悴。房應魁見他女兒這般光景，心里十分</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>骯臟，積得成病死了。剩下翠容母子二人，更加淒楚。這王詮自見翠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>容之手，心圖到手，苦于無方。聞說房守備已死，他生了一計。因長</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>安現任知縣是他父親的門生，就騎了一個極快的騾子，一日可行五六</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>百里，遂往長安縣去了。進得衙門，住了几天，知縣金日萃偶然說及</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石家這樁事來。王詮道：“石公子是弟的同進，且系對門。他變了產</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>業來賠修河工，料他不久就到了。但有句話不得不向世兄說知，石生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>為人甚是詭譎。完工之后，定叫他看守三年，才可放他回家。不然，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>偶有差失就累及世兄了。”金日萃應道：“相為之言，小弟自當銘心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”王詮又停留了几日，就回羅田縣來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石茂蘭來到西安府，落了店。差人投了文。次日早堂，見了太府</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，太府限他六個月完功。差人把石公子并銀子五千，押送長安縣去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>長安的知縣把銀子存庫。每日只發銀子二十五兩，著差人同石公子覓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>夫二百多名，往河上去修理。挑的挑，抉的抉，只消得一百四十五天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，就修的依舊如初了。剩下的銀子還有兩千，石生去領。長安縣開出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一本上司衙門使費的賬來，給石生看說：“剛剛足用并沒剩得分毫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”石生也不敢十分強要，親去稟知太府，工已告竣。太府驗過，把功</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>收訖。石生送了一個求回籍的稟帖，太府批道：“工雖已竣，尚須保</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>固三年，方許回籍。私逃者，拿回重責。”就把石生羈絆在此處了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>吃飯沒錢買，住店沒錢雇。只得在河岸上搭了一個窩鋪住著。日間在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>城里賣些字畫，落得錢數銀子，聊且糊口。晚上回到窩鋪里去睡。受</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了許多飢寒，嘗了無限苦楚。作詩以自傷，其詩曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    河工告峻不許還，身受艱辛几百般。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    異域無親誰靠戀，故鄉相隔多云山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    白晝街頭空擾擾，夜間臥聽水潺潺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    轉籌返旆在何日？心痛曷勝雨淚潸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生在外住過一年，王詮在家寫了一封假書，著人送到房宅，說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是石生的家報。翠容拆開一看，上寫道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    予自修河長安，操勞過度。飲食不均，積成一病。邇來日就垂危</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，料此生斷難重聚。賢妻年當青春，任爾自便，勿為我所誤。余言不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>宣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    拙夫石茂蘭手書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    翠容問家人道：“這書字是誰送來的？”那家人答道：“是西頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>王宅里人送來的。”翠容心里道：“孽畜是來行離間計了。”也寫了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一封回書道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    妾自丈夫西去，久已封發自守。此心不惟堅若金石，亦且皎如日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>月。但祈生渡玉門，以圖偕老。如有不諱，情甘就木。禽獸之行，斷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不肯為。臨啟曷勝愴淒之至。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    賤妾房翠容泣書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    寫完封好，著人送給王詮說：“這是石家娘子的家信，煩王大爺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>千萬托人捎到長安去。”王詮收下，拆開一看。知此計斷是不行了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>心中又畫了一策：“聽聞那劉氏夫人，夜間常起來焚香拜斗。再把這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個老媽治煞，單剩翠容，一個女子，斷難逃脫我手了。”主意拿定，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>他家有個家生子名喚黃虎。年紀二十多歲，甚是凶惡，且善于跳牆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>許了他五十兩銀子，叫他往房家去行刺。黃虎應允。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了次夜，黃虎拿了一個金剛圈。竟跳入房宅內院，轉過堂前一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>望，見劉氏夫人跪在地下，正磕頭拜斗哩。黃虎暗暗走到背后，一把</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>掀倒，使腳蹬住喉嚨。頓飯時間，把個劉氏夫人活活的捫死了。翠容</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>在房等候多時，不見他母親回去。起來看時，早已死了。叫人抬進屋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里，痛哭一場。天明料理喪事，不題。翠容想道：“害吾母者非他人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，定是王詮。”欲待鳴官，苦無憑証。且身系女流，不便出去。無奈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>何，忍氣吞聲，把劉氏夫人殯葬了。是時，正當八月盡間。一日，陰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>雨蒙蒙，金風颯颯。淒涼之狀，甚是難言。到得晚間，點起燈來，追</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>念雙親，懷想丈夫，滴了几點血淚。因題詩一首道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    征人一去路悠悠，孤守深閨已再秋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    萬里堤旁草漸蔓，望夫石畔水空流。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    游魚浮柬渺無望，飛雁銜書向誰投？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    憂思常縈魂夢內，几時相逢在重樓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    詩已題完，千思萬想，總是無路。長嘆道：“這等薄命，卻不如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>早死為妙。”遂取了一根帶子，拴在門上闌上。正伸頭時，忽見觀音</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>老母，左有金童，右有玉女，祥云靄靄，從空而降。把帶子一把扯斷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，叫道：“石娘子，為何起此短見？只因石生的魔障未消，你的厄期</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>未過。所以目下夫妻拆散。你的富貴榮華全在后半世哩。我教你兩句</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>要言：作尼莫犯比丘戎，遇僧須念彌陀經。這兩句話就可以全你的名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>節，保你的性命。切記勿忘。外有藥面一包，到萬難解脫時，你把這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>藥，向那人面上洒去。你好逃生。”翠容一一記清了。正要說話，那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>菩薩已騰空去了。翠容起來看時，桌上果有藥一包。上寫“催命丹”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>三字。仍舊包好，帶在身邊。出來焚香拜謝一番，方才回房。不題。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說王詮又生一計，使錢買著縣里的衙役，拿著一張假文來向翠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>容道：“石公子已經亡故，河工還未修完。現有長安縣的關文，叫家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里人去修完河工，以便收尸。翠容不知是計，認以為真，痛哭了一場</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。對差人道：“我家里實沒人來領尸，煩公差大哥回稟縣上老爺，給</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>轉一路回去罷。”差人道：“這也使的，但須有些使費。”翠容把首</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>飾等物，當了几兩銀子交與差人拿去。差人回向王詮道：“房小姐認</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>真石公子是死了。”住了些時，王詮著人來題媒，翠容不允。后又叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家人來討債，翠容答道：“我是一個女人，那有銀子還債。”王詮又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>行賄縣公，求替他追比這宗賬目。這羅田縣知縣，姓錢名為黨。是個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>利徒，就差了原差，飛簽火票，立拿房氏當堂回話。差人朝夕門口喊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>叫，房翠容那敢出頭。誰料禍不單行，房應魁做守備時，有一宗打造</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的銀子，私自使訖，并未奏銷清楚。上憲查出，聞其已死，行文著本</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>縣代為變產填補虧空。遂把他的宅子盡封去了。翠容只得賃了兩間房</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子，在里邊安身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    王詮見翠容落得這般苦楚，又托了他的一個姨娘姓毛，原是房家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的緊鄰。來向翠容細勸道：“你是少年婦人，如何能打官司？又沒銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子給他，萬一出官，體面安在？依我看來，你這等無依無靠，不如嫁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了他為妥。到了他家，那王詮斷不輕賤看你。”翠容轉想道：“菩薩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>囑付的言語，或者到了他家能報我仇，也未可知。”遂假應道：“我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>到了這般田地，也無可奈何了。任憑王家擺布罷。”毛氏得了這個口</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>角，就回信給王詮。次日，王詮就著他姨娘送過二十兩銀子來，叫翠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>容打整身面。怕他夫人不准，擇了一個好日子，把房翠容娶在另一處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>宅子上去。這正是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    真心要赴陽台會，卻成南柯夢一場。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說王詮到了晚間進房，把翠容仔細一看，真是十分美貌。走近</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>前來，意欲相調。翠容正色止住道：“我有話先向你說知，我丈夫石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生，與你何等相與。定要娶我，友誼安在？且我母親與你何仇，暗地</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>著人治死？”王詮道：“你我已成夫婦，往事不必再提。”翠容道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“咱二人實系仇家，何得不思雪夙恨。”遂把那藥面拿在手中，向王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>詮臉上一洒。那王詮哎喲一聲，當即倒地而死。翠容見王詮已死，打</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>開頭面箱子。把上好的金珠，包了一個包袱。約值千金，藏在懷中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>開了房門，要望路而走。忽然就地刮起一陣大風，把翠容刮在半虛空</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里，飄飄蕩蕩，覺著刮了有兩三千里，方才落下。風氣漸息，天色已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>明。抬頭看時，卻是觀音堂一座。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    進內一看，前邊一座大殿，是塑的佛爺。轉入后殿，里面是觀音</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>菩薩。盡后邊才是禪堂。從禪堂里走出一個老尼來，年近七旬。問道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“女菩薩，你是從何處來的？”房翠容答道：“妾是黃州府羅田縣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人。丈夫姓石，今夜被狂風刮來的。不知這是什么去處？離羅田縣有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>多少路程？”老尼道：“這是四川成都府城西，離城三里地。此去黃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>州，約有兩千多路。”翠容道：“奴家既到這里，斷難一時回家了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>情愿給師傅做徒弟罷。”老尼道：“我比丘家有五戒，守得這五戒，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>才可出的家。”翠容問道：“是那五戒？”老尼道：“目不視邪色，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>耳不聽邪聲，口不出邪言，足不走邪徑，心不起邪念。”翠容道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這五件，我都守得住。”老尼道：“你能如此，我給你閑房一座住著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。各自起火，早晚不過替我掃掃殿，燒燒香。除此以外，并無別事派</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>你了。若是愿意，你就住下。”翠容道：“這卻甚好。”遂拜老尼為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>師。折變了些首飾，以此渡日。翠容想道：“菩薩說，‘作尼莫犯比</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>丘戒’這句我明白了。‘遇僧須念彌陀經’，僧者，佛也。”就一日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兩次，來佛殿前焚香禱祝。不題。房翠容在外莫說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知茂蘭回來如何？再聽下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第七回  窮秀才故入陰魔障</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說石茂蘭看守河工三年，方才回家。進的城來，無處投奔。只</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>得先往岳丈家去看看。到了房宅門口，見物是人非。甚是驚異，打聽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>旁人說：“房守備夫婦俱沒了。他家小姐被王詮設法娶去。王詮已死</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，房小姐并不知歸往何處去了。這宅子是奉官變賣填補虧空了。”茂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>蘭聞說，大驚失色。回想：“不聽翠容之言，所以致有今日。”暗地</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里痛哭一場。前瞻后顧，無處扎腳。遂投城外客店里宿下。反復思想</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，欲還在此處住罷，這等落寞難見親朋。不如暫往襄陽，以便再尋生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>路。店里歇了一夜，次早就往襄陽府去了。到得襄陽，見那城郭宏整</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，人煙輻湊。居然又是個府會，比黃州更覺熱鬧。落到店中，歇了兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日。買了些紙來，畫了几張條山，寫了几幅手卷。逐日在街頭上去賣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，也落得些錢，暫且活生。一日，走到太平巷來，東頭路北第三家，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是胡員外的宅子。路南錯對門是個酒鋪，門上貼一付對聯道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    醉里乾坤大，壺中日月長。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生走近前來，就進酒鋪里坐下。酒保問道：“老客是要吃酒的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>嗎？”石生答道：“只要吃四兩。”那酒保把熱酒取過四兩來，給石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生斟上，就照管別的客去了。石生把酒吃完，還了酒錢。正要起身出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去，忽從店里邊跑出一個人來。卻是個長隨的打扮。問石生道：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這畫是賣的嗎？”石生答道：“正是。”那人把畫展開一看，夸道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“畫的委實不錯，這是樁什么故事？”石生道：“是朱虛后誅諸呂圖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”那人究問詳細，石生把當年漢家的故事說了一遍。并上面的詩句</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>也念給他聽了。那人道：“你這一張畫要多少錢？”石生答道：“憑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>太爺相贈便了。”那人從包里取出一塊銀子，約有三錢，遞給石生。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>揀了一張畫，卷好拿在手中。仍上里邊吃酒去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    此時，適值胡員外，在門首站著。把石生上下打量一番。想道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“我相此人，終須大貴。”遂走過來問道：“尊客是那邊來的呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石生答道：“在下是從黃州府羅田縣來的。”胡員外問道：“羅田縣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有個石嵐庵，你可認得他嗎？”石生答道：“就是先嚴。”胡員外道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“既然這樣，世兄是位公子了，如何流落到此處？”此時，石生不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>知道，方才那個買畫的是魏太監私訪的家人。就把他父親生前棄官，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>死后修河的事情逐一說了個清楚。都被那買畫的人，聽在心里去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>胡員外也把字畫拿過來一看，稱贊道：“世兄寫畫俱佳，甚屬可敬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>若不相棄，到舍下少敘片刻何如？”石生略不推辭，就隨著胡員外走</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    進得胡員外的院來，讓在西書房里坐下。叫人打整酒飯。胡員外</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>問道：“世兄曾進過學否？”石生答道：“已徼幸過了。”胡員外又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“世兄既經發軔，還該努力讀書，以圖上進，區區小成，何足終</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>身。”石生答道：“晚生非不有志前進，無奈遭際不幸，父母雙亡，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>夫妻拆散。家業凋零，不惟無以安身，并且難于糊口。讀書一事，所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>以提不起了。幸承老先生垂顧，相對殊覺赧顏。”胡員外道：“窮通</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>者人之常，這是無妨的。從來有志者事竟成。世兄果有意上進，讀書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>之資，就全在老夫身上。何如？”石生當下致謝不盡。待飯已畢，胡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>員外道：“念書須得個清淨書房，街西頭我有一處閑房，甚是僻淨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>先領你去看看，何如？”石生答道：“如此正妙。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    胡員外領著石生，家人拿著鑰匙，開了大門。進去走到客位，東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>山頭上有個小角門，里邊是一個大院子。正中有個養魚池，池前是一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>座石山子。山子前是兩大架葡萄。池北邊有前后出廊的瓦房三間，是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>座書房。前面挂著“芸經堂”三字一面匾。屋里東山頭上，有個小門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，進去是兩間暖書房，卻甚明亮。后邊有泥房三間是個廚屋，廚屋前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有兩珠垂楊，后邊有几棵桃樹，兩株老松，一池竹子。石生看完，胡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>員外道：“這個去處，做個書房何如？”石生答道：“極好。”胡員</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>外道：“世兄若愛中了此處，今晚暫且回店。明日我就著人打掃，后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日你就搬過來罷了。但大門時常關鎖，出入不便。從東邊小胡同里，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>另開一門，你早晚出入便可自由了。”石生謝道：“多煩老先生操心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”遂別過胡員外而去，不題。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說胡員外到了次日，就叫人另開了一個小門。把書房里打掃干</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>淨，專候石生搬來。到了第三日，石生從新買的書籍筆硯，自家拿著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。叫人擔著鋪蓋，直走到書房里邊，方才放下，時當炎暑天氣。西山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>頭上鋪著一張小床，把鋪蓋擱在上面。前檐上，一張八仙桌子，把書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>籍筆硯擺在上頭。胡員外進來看了一看，說道：“這卻也罷了。”又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“世兄既在此住扎，你我就是一家人了。晴明天氣賣些字畫，或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>可糊口。倘或陰天下雨，難出門時，老夫自別有照應，斷勿相拘。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石生再三致謝，說完同著胡員外鎖了門，仍往街上去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    胡員外回到家來，向夫人馮氏說道：“我看石公子日后定是大發</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。佳婿之說，大約應在此人了。但不知二女從何而出？”夫人答道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“渺冥之事，未必果應，這也不必多說。”再說石生到了街上，又賣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了几張字畫。天色已黑，買了一枝蠟燭，潑了一壺熱茶，來到門首，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>開了鎖進來。關上門，走到屋里。把燭點上一看，書籍筆硯俱沒有了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。心中驚異道：“門是鎖著，何人進來拿去？”吃著茶，坐了一會。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>譙樓上，已鼓打二更了。忽聽得，東山頭上角門響了一聲。從里邊走</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>出一個女子來，年紀不過十八九歲。兩手捧著書籍，姍姍來前，仍舊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>把書籍放在桌上。你說這女子是什么光景？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    人材一表，兩鬢整齊。烏云繚繞，柳腰桃腮。美目清皎，口不點</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>唇，蛾眉淡掃。金蓮步來三回轉，卻只因鞋弓襪小。何等樣標致，怎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>般的窈窕。細看來，真真是世上絕無人間少。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    ──右調《步步嬌》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    又見一個女子，年不過二八。雙手捧著筆硯，裊裊而至。照樣放</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>在原舊去處。你說這個女子是何等模樣？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    面龐員漫細長身，鬢發如云。鬢勻髻高半尺頭上戴，金蓮三寸不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>沾塵。口輔兒端好，眸子兒傳神。丰姿甚可人。又雖不是若耶溪邊浣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>紗女，卻宛似和番出塞的王昭君。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    ──右調《耍孩兒》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    這兩個女子站在桌前，石生麾之不去。問道：“你莫非是兩個鬼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>嗎？”彼此相視而笑。少頃，走近前來，把石生雙目封住。石生全然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不怕，極力掙開。又把燭吹滅，石生從新點上。鬧有半夜，石生身覺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>困倦，倒在床上。二女子把他抬著屋里走了一遭，依舊放在床上。石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生只當不覺。時將雞叫，二女子方回豎頭屋里去了。只聽得兩個女子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>笑著說道：“石郎如此膽量，定當大成。吾等得所托矣。”到了次晚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，石生又在外回來。點上燭時，二女子仍舊在桌旁站候。石生問道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“你兩個是要做么？”二女子答道：“俺要念書。”石生道：“我且</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>問你，你二人是何名姓？”只見那個大的答道：“我叫秋英。”小的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>答道：“我叫春芳。”再問其姓氏，俯而不答。石生道：“你既要念</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>書，須得書籍。”二女子答道：“都有。”石生先寫字數行，叫兩女</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子來認一遍。認去無不字字記得清楚。石生道：“你兩個卻也念的書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”二女子轉入屋里，各拿四書一部出來上學。石生問道：“你各人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>能念多少呢？”二女子答道：“能念兩冊。”號上兩冊，一個時辰就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來背書，卻是甚熟。教他寫字，出手就能成個。石生甚是驚訝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    又一日晚間，春芳領著一個唇紅齒白七八歲的幼童走進門來。見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了石生就跪下磕頭。石生問道：“這又是誰？”春芳答道：“這是我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的兄弟，名喚馗兒，特來上學。望先生收留下他。”石生道：“這那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有不收之理。”春芳送一紅紙封套給石生。石生問道：“這是什么？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”春芳答道：“是馗兒的贄見，先生收下罷。日后還有用處。”石生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>打開一看卻是金如意一支。遂叫馗兒過來號書。念的比那兩個女子更</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>多。叫他寫字，寫的比那兩個女子更好。沒消一月的工夫，三個的四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>書俱各念完。號上經典沒消半年，五經皆通。講書作文，開筆就能成</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>章。一年之后，文章詩賦，三個俱無不精通。一日晚間，石生向三個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>徒弟道：“爾等從我將近二年，學問料有近益。我各出對聯一句，你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>們務要對工，以見才思。遂先召春芳出一聯云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    紅桃吐葩艷陽早占三春日，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    春芳不待思想順口對道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    綠柳垂線繁陰遍遮四夏天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    又召秋英出一聯云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    竹有箭松有筠歷風霜而葉柯不改，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    秋英也順口對道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    金在熔石在璞經琢煉而光彩彌彰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    又召馗兒出一聯云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    設几席以程材提耳命面幸逢孺子可教，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    馗兒也接口對道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    望門牆而受業淑陶漸摩欣被先生之風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生夸道：“你三個對的俱甚工穩，足見竿頭進步。”自此以后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，師徒四人相處，倏忽間二載有余。這石生在外鰥居已久，見二女子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>又是絕色美貌。未免有些欣羨之意，時以戲言挑之。二女子厲色相拒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“你我現系師徒，師徒猶父子也。遽萌苟且之心，豈不有忝名教</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，自誤前程。勸先生斷勿再起妄念。”石生見其詞嚴義正，游戲之言</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，從此不敢說了。石生與二女子，雖有幽明，卻同一家。只石生自己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>知道，總不向人說出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知后來終能隱昧否？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第八回  富監生誤投陷人坑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說石生夜間教書一事，雖不肯向人說出，然亦終難隱昧。太平</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>巷東北鼓棚街上，有一個黌門監生，姓蔡名寅字敬符。家道殷富。太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>平巷西頭面北大街有他綢緞鋪一個，本錢約有六七千金。日逐上鋪，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>定經過石生齋前。又常買他的字畫，因此與石生相熟。一日晚上回家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，走至石生書齋。聞里面書聲朗朗，并非一兩人的聲音。蔡寅心中異</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>樣道：“石九畹只他自己，何念書者之多也？莫非收了几個徒弟嗎？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”到了次日，街上遇見石生問道：“九畹兄近日收了几位高徒？”石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生答道：“只弟孤身一人，有甚徒弟？”蔡寅道：“莫要瞞我。”石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生道：“你若不信，自管來看。”蔡寅終是疑惑。又一日晚間來到此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>處，竟把門叫開，到屋里看了一看。果然只是石生，并無別人，心上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>愈加驚異。暗暗想道：“石九畹器宇軒昂，學殖深厚，或者后當發跡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，默有鬼神相助，也說不定。”從此見了石生分外的親敬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    蔡寅有個妹子，年屆十六。姿色傾城，尚未許人。蔡寅向他母親</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>說道：“石公子目下雖然厄窮，日后定然發跡，不如托人保親，把妹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子許了他為妥。”其母答道：“石生半世淪落，何時運轉。婚姻大事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，不可苟且。我自留心，給他擇配。這事你卻不必多管。”蔡寅閉口</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>而退。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    一日蔡寅在鋪內算賬，過晚回家，時已鼓打二更。走到石生齋前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，聽得內里書聲，不忍舍去，又聽了半個時辰。轉身走到太平巷東頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，剛才往北一拐，路旁過來了四個棍徒，上前攔住道：“蔡大爺怎晚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>才回家嗎？”蔡寅答道：“正是。”那一個說：“天還不甚晚，請蔡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>大爺到舍下坐坐，俺去送你。”遂把蔡寅領到一個背巷里去。那人叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>開大門，讓蔡寅進去。蔡寅留心一看，見不是個好去處，撤身要走。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>那里容得，只見四個人把蔡寅推推搡搡，架到屋里。外邊的門戶俱關</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>鎖了。蔡寅見他四個甚是凶惡，也就不敢十分強走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    那人把蔡寅延至上座，他四個在兩旁相陪。大酒大肉，登時吃起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。蔡寅說道：“弟與兄等雖系同城，未曾識面。叨承厚擾，何以相報</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。請問兄等尊姓大名，異日好相稱呼。”這個說：“我叫秦雄西。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>那一個說：“我叫楚旺南。”一個說：“我是魯挾山。”一個說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>我是齊超海。”秦雄西道：“俺四個系拜的把子，俱是肝膽義氣朋友</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，素聞蔡爺的大名，故斗膽邀來一敘。”說話中間從里面走出兩個妓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>女來。楚旺南叫道：“你兩個過來，陪著蔡爺吃酒。俺們轉一轉來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”二妓女走到蔡寅面前，深深道了個萬福。就坐在兩旁。那四人轉入</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里面去了。蔡寅問道：“二位美人尊姓台號呢？”大的答道：“賤妾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>姓白名喚玉琢。”小的答道：“賤妾姓黃名喚金鑲。”蔡寅見了這兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個妓女，不覺神魂飄蕩。二妓女又極力奉承，就吃的酒有七八分了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>蔡寅道：“你我三人猜枚行令，還未盡興。如有妙調見賜一二，方暢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>予懷。”玉琢道：“蔡爺若不嫌聒噪，賤妾就要獻丑了。”遂口唱一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>曲道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    紗窗兒照照，卸殘妝，暫把熏籠靠。好叫我心焦躁。月轉西樓，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>還不見才郎到。燈光兒閃閃，漏聲兒迢迢。怎長夜几時，叫奴熬到雞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>三號。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    ──右調《蝶戀花》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    玉琢唱完金鑲也道：“賤妾也相和一曲。蔡爺千萬莫笑。”蔡寅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“陽春白雪傾耳不暇，那有相笑之理。”金鑲遂口唱一曲道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    盼玉人不來，玉人來時，闖滿懷。解解奴的羅襦，托托奴的香腮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。你好風流，我好貪愛。顧不得羞答答上牙床，暫且勾了這筆相思債</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    ──右調《滿江紅》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    唱完。蔡寅夸獎不已。又略飲几杯，遂把蔡寅引到后邊一座房子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里去。兩邊俱是板斷間，俱有鋪的床鋪。當門桌上，一邊放著骰盆，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一邊放著牌包。二妓女道：“妾等聞蔡爺仗義疏財，是個丈夫。無非</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>邀來玩玩，以求相幫之意。請蔡爺上座，俺們下面奉陪。”蔡寅只得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過去坐下。兩個妓女緊靠著蔡寅。秦雄西在旁打頭，那三個在下面襯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>局。把骰盆擱在當中，十兩一柱。從蔡寅起首輪流擲去。骰是鉛的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>三個搭勾，同局一個，蔡寅如在夢中。待到五更時分蔡寅已輸了一千</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>二百余兩。二妓道：“夜已太深，叫蔡爺歇息歇息罷。”就叫蔡寅在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>東間里床上睡了。那四人各自散去。二妓女把門關了，解衣上床，與</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>蔡寅相偎相抱而睡。蔡寅熬的已是困乏，又被二妓纏身。直睡到次日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>飯后，方才起來。意欲要走，二妓道：“蔡爺早飯未用，前賬未結斷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，走不的。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    蔡寅沒法叫齊超海拿著他的手帖，到綢鋪中，兌了一千二百多兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>銀子，把前賬結清。抽身走時，又被二妓女拉住不准出門。蔡寅在此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一連住了十晝十夜，把一個綢緞鋪的本錢盡輸給四個棍徒了。二妓女</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>向那四人道：“蔡爺在咱家破鈔已多，晚上叫他回家去罷。”到得一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>更多時，楚旺南打燈籠，那三個兩旁相跟。蔡寅與二妓作別，出門而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去。走了一會，蔡寅見走的不是舊路。問道：“這是往那里去的？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>楚旺南答道：“從這里上東去，再走一道南北街，往東一拐就是宅上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了。”正走著，只見一個人問道：“蔡大爺來了么？”魯挾山指著蔡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>寅道：“這就是。”那人先跑下去了。蔡寅問道：“這是何人？”楚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>旺南答道：“那是敝友。”秦雄西道：“天還早著哩，咱到他家吃會</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子茶，再送你未遲。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    蔡寅就跟他們，進了那家的大門，從里邊走出一個老媽來，問道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“那是蔡爺？”蔡寅答道：“區區便是。”老媽便讓到客位里，蔡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>寅進得客位一看，見燈燭輝煌。卻像個請客的光景。老媽陪著蔡寅茶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>未吃完，那四個人俱偷溜了。蔡寅抬身要走，老媽留道：“蔡爺既肯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>下顧，那有走的道理？”蔡寅看看外門又俱鎖了，只得回來坐下。因</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>問道：“媽媽尊姓呢？”老媽答道：“老身姓沈叫做三媽，原是門戶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人家。因小女桂娘，羨慕蔡爺才貌，知今晚從此經過，特留下一會。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>秀香，叫你三姑娘出來。”只見一個十四五歲的丫鬟打著燈籠，后面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>跟著一個女子，年紀不過二十以上。真有沉魚落雁之容，閉月羞花之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>貌。走近前來，拜了一拜。就在蔡寅旁邊坐了。說道：“賤妾久慕蔡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>爺的才貌，今得一會。可謂三生有幸。”蔡寅答道：“陋貌俗態，何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>堪上攀仙子。”老媽道：“請坐席罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    于是延蔡寅上座，桂娘在旁，老媽下面相陪。酒是好酒，菜是好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>菜。霎時，席冷。蔡寅把桂娘仔細看來，比那兩個妓女更覺標致。早</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有心猿意馬拴索不住之意。老媽到也知趣，叫道：“秀香，夜深了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>送你姑爺姑娘上樓去罷。”丫鬟前邊引著，蔡寅與桂娘攜手并肩，登</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>入樓中。是夜，顛鸞倒鳳妙難備述。自此以后，你貪我愛。蔡寅那里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>還想的起家來。是月梨花正開，院內有白梨花一樹。蔡寅向桂娘指著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“美人能作詩否？即以白梨花為題。”桂娘答道：“頗曉大略，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>聊且草就，再乞蔡爺斧政。”遂拈筆題七言律一首。上寫道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    冰肌煥彩凝柔條，玉骨噴香散早朝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    淡妝無煩洛下沈，粉葩寧許畫工描。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    一枝帶雨姿誠秀，萬朵臨風色更嬌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    雪態紛披人耀目，艷紅那些比桃天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    題完，蔡寅看了稱贊不已。住有月余。桂娘道：“蔡爺到此已久</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，也該往家里看看去了。”蔡寅道：“美人說得極是。”遂叫了老媽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來算賬。老媽道：“姑爺咱是下樣的親，如何提的起錢來？”讓到十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>分盡頭，老媽說道：“姑爺既然不肯，給老身回几票當罷。”午間設</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>席，給蔡寅餞行。席終之后，老媽拿出几個當票來，遞與蔡寅。蔡寅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>接過一看，本利共該銀三千余兩。只得應允道：“我回家不過半月，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>就贖出送來。”又與桂娘留戀了一會，彼此才洒淚而別。蔡寅回到家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>中，他母親還不怎樣。室人褚氏，因其花費銀錢，貪戀妓女，心中暗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>惱，自縊而死。發送已過。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    蔡寅當地數頃，把當票贖出。親自跟著，叫人送去。老媽喜其信</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>實，又留他住下。晚間上的樓來，桂娘問道：“蔡爺你穿的誰的服孝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>？”蔡寅答道：“拙荊新亡，出殯未久。”說罷，不覺泣下。桂娘道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“你人亡家敗，俱是被俺這老媽所致。”蔡寅問道：“這卻怎說？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”桂娘道：“自始至終，俱是這個老媽串通那四個棍徒，先著玉琢金</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>鑲兩個下腳貨，引你入溝。后叫賤妾把你占住，坑你的銀子，共計起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來大約有萬金了。我卻不沒良心，我本良家女子，誤落水中。你若肯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>把我贖出，你奮志去讀書。這花費的銀子，我俱照數還你。”蔡寅道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“目下手中無錢奈何？”桂娘道：“我是八百銀子買的，但能結（</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>借）得八百銀子來，把我贖出，我自有銀子還他。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    蔡寅念戀桂娘的才色，次日回到家里托人結了八百銀子，親自帶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>到桂娘家來。桂娘就轉托魏二姑向沈三媽贖身。沈三媽應允。蔡寅把</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>八百兩銀子交清。桂娘向沈三媽道：“孩兒給母親弄錢多年，今日出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去，別的不要。兩個頭面箱子井鋪蓋枕頭我要帶去。”沈三媽道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這值几何，任憑你帶。”桂娘當下謝過三媽，收拾了，上了轎子。直</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>投鼓棚街而來。到了蔡寅家中，桂娘把箱子打開，枕頭拆破，叫蔡寅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一看。盡是金珠等物，共值萬有余金。蔡寅從此恢復家產，奮志讀書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。這桂娘在蔡寅家改邪歸正，也極善于事奉婆婆，接待小姑，合家之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人無不歡喜。蔡寅遂以繼室相視，終身不再娶了。蔡寅之事已畢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知石生在書房如何？再聽下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第九回  應考試系身黃州獄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說魏太監的家人，買得石生墨畫一張。原要回京獻給主人。及</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>私訪已完，回到京中，把這幅畫獻上。魏太監著人懸之“芳草軒”中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。家人把石生告訴胡員外的話，詳細說了一遍。魏太監卻也不擱在心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>上。一日，光祿寺正卿馬克昌謁見。魏忠賢引至軒中，來觀此畫。馬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>克昌遂把上面詩句，口中一一念道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    安邦自古賴賢豪，群奸雜登列滿朝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    幸得手持三尺劍，愿為當代鋤草茅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    馬克昌把詩念完，向魏忠賢冷笑道：“大人你看這詩，分明是以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>群奸譏殫吾等。以朱虛侯、劉章自任。如此輕薄，殊屬可惡。但沒落</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>款，不知是誰人寫畫的？”家人在旁便答道：“這人姓石名茂蘭，是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>羅田縣秀才。他父親曾做過長安縣知縣。后升廣西柳州府知府。”魏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>忠賢道：“這一定是石峨的兒子了。罷了，罷了。他父親違吾鈞旨，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>棄官竊逃，我卻不十分追究。他反敢這樣刻薄，我斷不與他干休。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>馬克昌勸道：“些須小事，漫圖報復。”彼此相別而去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說湖廣，選了一個學院。姓韓名嵋字仰山。為人甚無行止，是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>魏忠賢的門生。臨赴任時，來參見老師。魏忠賢囑托道：“黃州府羅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>田縣有個秀才姓石名茂蘭。他與我有夙嫌，你考黃州時，替我拿獲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>解到京來。”韓嵋應諾而去，不題。到了八月中秋，石生此日，在街</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>上賣字畫。見一伙趕棚的人，商量起身的日期。石生問道：“眾位是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>要上那府里去的？”那人答道：“學院按臨黃州，行文九月十二日調</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>齊，十六日下馬。”石生道：“這信果真嗎？”那人道：“俺親使管</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的閂師傅說，如何不真？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生聞得此信，因是節下，買了几樣菜果，打了一瓶煮酒。拿到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>齋中，晚間點上燭時。秋英等已在席前侍立。石生俱命坐下，把酒肴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>擺上，幽明均享了一會。石生見秋英容顏姣好，心中到底有些羨慕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>因說道：“今晚星月皎潔，誠屬佳境。每人詠詩一首，以寫雅懷。或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>從月光生情，或就星辰寓意。起句內或明用或暗用，定要有個照字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>韻腳不必拘定。秋英道：“請從先生起韻，俺們隨后步去。”石生遂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>口詠一詩道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    一輪明月照天中，欲會女霜路莫通。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    玉杵空有誰送去，竊思跳入廣寒宮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    此詩言雖慕二女之容，終苦無緣到手。秋英口詠一詩道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    漢光散彩射樓牆，織女投梭不自忙。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    橋填須當乞巧日，愿君暫且效牛郎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    此詩言雖有佳期，還須待時。春芳也口詠一詩道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    一天列宿照當頭，妄羨中宮命不猶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    奉賦小星三五句，何嫌宵行抱衾ヤ。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    此詩言正房既有人占去，即列側室亦所甘心。馗兒口詠一詩道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    月光東上映西廂，金殿風飄桂子香。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但得側身王母宴，應看仙娥捧壽觴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    此詩言果能讀書前進，何患二女終難到手。詠詩已畢。石生道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“你們各自散去。我歇息半夜，明日好打點回家。”秋英問道：“先</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生回家何干？”石生答道：“我去應歲考。”馗兒道：“先生斷不可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去，一去定有大禍。俟轉歲補考罷。”石生不聽，一定要去。三個極</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>力相勸，直說到雞叫頭遍。見石生到底不允，三個方才散去。石生也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>方就寢。到了次日，石生收拾妥了行李，又為三徒派下些工夫。把門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>鎖上，鑰匙交與胡宅收著，天夕出城落店。次早起五更，直回黃州去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說這個韓學院，下馬來到黃州，下學放告已畢。挂牌考人，羅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>田縣就是頭棚。五鼓點名時，點到石生，茂蘭接過卷子要走。學院叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>住問道：“原任柳州府知府石峨是你何人？”石生應道：“是生員的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>父親。”學院道：“你現今身負重罪，可知道嗎？”石生應道：“生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>員委系不知。”學院道：“此時也不暇與你細說。”傳黃州府著人押</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去送監。俟考竣時，審問解京。黃州府就著人把石生押送監中去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這石生坐在監中，白日猶可，到了晚間，鎖拷得甚是難受。欲要打點</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，手無半文。暗想：“自己無甚過犯，緣何遭此奇禍。”直哭到三更</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>時分，方才住聲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    是時監內人犯，俱各睡熟。禁卒也暫去安歇。石生忽聽得門外一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>陣風響，睜眼一看，卻是秋英、春芳領著馗兒，三個從外哭泣而來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>走到跟前，秋英道：“先生不聽俺勸，果有此禍。俺也不能替你了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>俺回去代先生告狀鳴冤罷。先生務要保重自己，勿起短見。這是銀子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>二十多兩，先生收住，以便買些茶飯，打點打點禁卒。”石生道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>我不聽良言，自投法網，反蒙爾等來照看，愧悔無及了。”秋英道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“這也不必，原是先生前定之數。俺們回去罷，說話太長，驚醒旁人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，反覺不便。”石生把銀子收下，他三個又哭著去了。石生在監不題</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說三個鬼徒回到家中，秋英寫了一張陰狀，往城隍台下去告，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>狀云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    具稟秋曲，為代師鳴冤。乞天電察，以正誣枉事，切照。身師石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>茂蘭，系黃州府羅田縣廩生。今被學憲大人，拿送監中。尋其根由，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>實系太監魏賊所唆。似此無故被冤，法紀安在。哀懇本府城隍太老爺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>垂憐苦衷，施以實報，焚頂無既。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    馗兒寫了一張陽狀，上巡撫案下去告。上寫道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    具稟馗兒，為辨明冤枉，以救師命事。切照。身師石茂蘭系黃州</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>府羅田縣廩生。與魏太監，素無宿嫌，竟唆撥學台大人，拿送監內，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>性命難保。為此哀懇本省撫憲大人，辨明冤枉，救出師命，銜感無既</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    寫完，彼此細看了一遍。秋英向春芳道：“妹子，你年紀尚小，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不可出門，在家里看家罷。我先去城隍台下告一張狀，看是如何？再</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>叫馗兒上撫院衙門里去。”籠了籠頭面，整了整衣襟。把狀子藏在懷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里，出門往城隍廟前去了。凡在城隍台下告狀者，必先到土地司里挂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了號，方才准送。秋英來到土地司里挂了號，拿著狀子往外正走。遇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>見一個鬼卒，問道：“這位娘子如此妙年，又這等標致，難道家中就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>無別人，竟親自出來告狀？”秋英把代師鳴冤的情由說與他聽。那鬼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>卒稱道：“看來，你卻是女中的丈夫，這狀子再沒有不准的。但城隍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>老爺今日不該坐堂，面遞是沒成的了。一會收發狀詞，必定是蕭判爺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。我對你說，蕭判爺性子凶暴。倘或問話，言語之間須要小心。如惹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>著他，無論男女，盡法究處，甚是利害。”說完，這個鬼卒就走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>秋英聽得這話，欲待回去，來是為何？欲去遞時，恐難近前。籌度再</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>三，硬著膽子，徑向城隍廟門口去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    住不多時，從里往外喊道﹔“判爺已坐，告狀的進來，挨次投遞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。再候點名。”秋英聽說跟著眾人，往里直走，抬頭一看，只見儀門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>旁邊，坐著一位判官。鐵面紫髯，□目皤腹。殺氣凜凜，十分可畏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>秋英遞過狀去，站在一邊伺候。卻說這位判官，姓蕭名秉剛。乃漢時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>蕭何之后，生前為人粗率，行事卻無私曲。死后以此成神。家中有一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>位夫人名叫俏丟兒，原是個疥癩女鬼。容顏雖好，身上總有些瘢痕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>因此蕭判官頗不稱心，意欲物色一個出色的女子，招為二房。屢次尋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>覓，總是沒有。那夫人窺透其意，往往家中不安。今晨正從家中斗氣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>而來，心中不靜。故秋英遞狀時，未暇觀其容色。及挨次點名，點到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>秋英。抬頭一看，驚訝道：“何物殊尤，幸到吾前。”停筆問道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>你是那里的女鬼，為何在此告狀？一一說清，方准你的狀詞。”秋英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>跪下稟道：“奴乃浙江紹興府，焦寧馨之女，奴父同姑丈秦可大作幕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>襄陽。住在太平巷徐家房子內，表妹春芳、表弟馗兒，俱系與奴同病</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>而亡。走至閻王殿前，閻王爺分付道：你姊妹二人日后該在此處成一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>段奇緣，不該你們脫生。奴等回來，在此處專候。并表弟馗兒，現今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>還同在一塊里居住。生員石茂蘭是奴等的業師，無故被魏賊陷害。所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>以奴家代師鳴冤，望判爺千萬垂憐。”判官道：“我看你這般的容顏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，恁小的年紀。正該嫁人投主，以圖終身的大事。奇緣之成，是在何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>時。況且你身又系女流，讀什么詩書，認什么師長。一派胡說。你的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>狀是斷然不准的。”叫鬼卒把這個女子扶入我衙門里去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    鬼卒得令，就拉的拉，扯的扯，把一個秋英女子，直推到判官衙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>內去了。蕭判官收狀發放已過，回到本衙內，叫過秋英來。分付道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“本廳叫你到此，別無他意。因你的容顏，頗中我心。我意欲招你為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>二房夫人，同享富貴，斷莫錯了主意。”秋英并不答應，說之再三，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>秋英方回道：“判爺你系居官，安得圖謀良家女子為妾，致干天條。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>且奴與石生系有夙緣，豈忍從此而舍彼。這樁事是再沒有說頭的。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>蕭判官見秋英不從，便當下威逼道：“我的刑罰，甚是利害。料你一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個女流，如何當得。我百般拷打，不如早早的從下罷。”秋英聽了大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>怒，便厲聲道：“判爺你若是強相逼迫，我雖不能當下雪恨，寧無異</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日。萬一我若得見了城隍，定然叫你粉尸萬段。”說罷大罵不止。判</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>官聽說大怒，要著人來打。又恐夫人里面聽見，再惹氣生。分付鬼卒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，把秋英且監在別處一座閑房里。一日三次拷打，且按下不題。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說春芳馗兒在家候至兩日，并不見秋英回去。心里發悶，親自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來到城隍府前打聽。才知秋英被蕭判官監在屋里不能回家了。春芳回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來向馗兒一說，馗兒拿著狀子，徑投撫院門前去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    不知馗兒一去如何？看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>         第一十回  鳴師冤質訟督憲堂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說馗兒到得撫院門前，打聽了一番。撫院并不出門，又非放告</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的日期，無路可投。只得把信炮點著了一個。一聲響時，里邊大人聽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的炮響，霎時升堂。開了大門，聲聲喊道：“鳴冤人投進。”馗兒不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>慌不忙，走進前來。只見堂規威嚴，人役森列。暖閣內坐著一位大人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。馗兒近前跪下說﹔“民子初開，向上一遭。”早有茶房接去，送在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>公案桌上。大人從頭看了一遍問道：“你是何處的人，石生緣何叫你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>替他告狀？”馗兒回道：“小人是襄陽府城里人，石生系小人的師父</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。他現在監中，家中并無別人。因此小人代師鳴冤，望大人垂鑒。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>撫院道：“你怎小小的年紀，卻敢這樣放刁。魏大人在京都，石生視</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>□□風馬牛不相及。石生被獄，或為別事。你說系魏大人唆撥，那是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>憑証？”馗兒回道：“魏太監專權弄勢，人所共曉。因去歲魏太監的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家人，買去身師畫圖一張。上面有題得律詩四句。詩中有群奸草茅等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>字。他就說是譏誚的他。轉托學院，把身師拿到監里。考完時還要解</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>京究處。小人所供，俱是實話。并無半句誣捏。”撫院道：“依你所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>供，是一派的胡說。著人給我推出門去。”人役聽說遂把馗兒拉著，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>向外就走。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    撫院猛然看見，馗兒在日光之下走著，并無照的人影。便立刻叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“快把他帶回來。”馗兒聽說，轉身回到堂前。從新復又跪下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>撫院發怒道：“從來陰鬼無影，本院坐的是朝廷法堂。你是那里的山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>精水怪，白日青天，竟敢在此胡鬧。”叫“左右給我拉下去打。”左</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>右人役，把馗兒扯翻在地。喝聲“行杖”打下一板去，是一股白氣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>打到三十，并無半聲叫。及至放起距躍曲踴，倍覺精神。撫院大怒，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>叫聲：“給我夾起來。”人役聽說，將馗兒放倒，把腿填在夾棍里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>直夾了有三個時辰，方才解去。馗兒神色依然如初。撫院道：“這分</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>明是鬼無疑了。”著家人到宅內取出天師禁鬼符一道，貼在馗兒胸前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。又用紙使印一塊粘在馗兒背后。從來陰鬼，原怕天師的法符，朝廷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的印信。竟把馗兒一時制的不能動轉了。遂著人送入監中。分付禁卒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，留心看守。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說馗兒在監中，坐到三更時分。揭去身上的符印，逃出監來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>正要尋個去路。忽聽得街上傳鑼響亮，人役喝道之聲：卻是本省城隍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>出來巡街。唬的馗兒躲藏在個更棚里。城隍走的相近，叫聲“住轎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”分付鬼卒道：“此處有什么冤鬼，竟致得怨氣沖天。給我搜來。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>鬼卒過去一搜，就把馗兒帶到轎前，跪在地下。城隍問道：“你是何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>方的游魂，敢在這個去處作怪。”馗兒就把石生被害，并他代為鳴冤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的情由，一一察知城隍。城隍道：“據你所供，這番意氣卻有可取。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>但你的年紀，甚是幼小。常在陰司里飄飄蕩蕩，何年是個出頭的日子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。依本府看來，不如把你送在一個富貴人家，脫生去罷。”馗兒問道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“蒙太爺垂憐，小人感恩不盡。但小人有兩個姐姐，現在襄陽。業</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>師石生，還在監中。小的轉生以后，就再不得見面了。”說罷，痛哭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。城隍又分付道：“你也不必如此悲戚。你那兩個姐姐與石生系有夙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>緣。不久，即成夫婦。剩你自己，何處歸宿。魏賊一干奸人，不久禍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>事將近臨頭，冤也不必你鳴。你姊妹師徒，日后重逢有期，無煩過為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>留戀。“叫鬼卒把他送到杭州府錢塘縣里，程翰林家投胎托生去罷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”鬼卒得令，領著馗兒，起陣陰風，一直去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>    卻說程翰林名謙，學S光。是一個翰林院侍講。曾點過兩次主考</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，做過一任學院。因他母親年邁，告終養老回家。年紀不過五十歲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>一妻一妾。夫人蘇氏，生得一子，名喚程誘蝖C生來姿質魯笨，念書</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>念到十七八歲，總不明白。屢次應考，盡落空網。程翰林在前也不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道他兒子是個何等樣的學問。及至回家，逐日盤問。方才知他不通。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>凡做一篇文字，功夫必須兩天。程翰林也懶于給他改抹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    側室柳氏身懷重妊。八月十三日，夜間時當分娩。蘇氏夫人聽說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，著人請下穩婆。房中點上燈燭。叫丫頭媽媽，緊緊在旁邊伺候。他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>也不住的時來照看。鬼卒領著馗兒的靈魂，早在門外等候。及至時辰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>將到，鬼卒把門上的帘子一掀，馗兒往里看時，只見床上坐著一個少</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>年婦人。聲聲叫疼，旁邊一個穩婆緊相依靠。住的卻是朱紅亮s的好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>房子，才到回頭，被那鬼卒一把推到床上。呱的一聲，早已投胎落草</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了。穩婆抱起來看，乃是一男。蘇氏夫人不勝歡喜，遂報喜于程翰林</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>。程翰林也甚是欣幸，就起名叫做程輓驉C馗兒投生之時，卻未曾喝</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過迷魂湯，心里極是清白的，但輕易不敢說話。過了三朝、滿月，漸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>漸的添了些見識，卻總不想家。長到一兩歲，只會認人，不能出語。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>程翰林夫婦恐真是個啞子了，卻也無從問他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    一日，程翰林與程誘蝳b書房里講書。家人來請吃午飯，適值程</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>輓鬫b書房中玩耍。心中想道：“我哥哥年紀已過二十，連個學還不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>能進。必定是文章不好，我找出來看看方妥。遂把外門關上，走到屋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里，上到椅子上。就書里翻出三篇沒動筆的文章來，看了一遍。不覺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>大笑道：“這等文字，無怪乎不能進學。”就磨了磨墨，把筆膏了膏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，大批大抹，頃刻之間，把三篇文章登時看完。末后題了一首七言律</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>詩，以代總評。其詩云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    軋茁殊屬太支離，外落孫山固所宜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    書讀五車方為富，文成七步始稱奇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    少年不受懸梁苦，老歲無聞后悔遲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    從此問津尚未晚，將來應有入彀時。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    評完了，卻把三篇文章仍舊放在書里。下來椅子，開了門，就往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>院里去了。卻說程翰林吃飯已完，領著程誘蝖A仍來書房里坐下。程</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>誘蝔ㄔL的書放的不是原舊去處。便拿過來，掀開一看。見三篇文章</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，俱經動了筆。心中詫異道：“這是何人，敢來作踐我。”就送與他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>父親一看，程翰林觀其批評恰當，詩句明白。但字畫不成個頭。心里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>也甚是異樣。遂叫看門的來問道：“我去吃飯有何人書房里來？”看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>門的回道：“并無外人，只二相公進來。關上了門，玩了一會，就開</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>門出去，上院里走了。”程翰林心里疑惑道：“沒的就是他不成？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>回到院內，叫過程輓魖荂C追問道：“你哥哥書房中的文章，是你給</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>他看的么？”程輓鬙u是搖頭。程翰林道：“夫人，你再仔細問他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”蘇氏夫人，千方百計，嚇逼不過。不覺開口應道：“是孩兒偶然作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>孽。叫父親大人不必疑怪。”程翰林夫婦二人，見程輓髐f能說話，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>且通文理，心中又驚又喜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    一日，程翰林考問程輓髐飛g左史，以及諸子百家等書。左右根</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>尋，總盤詰不住。程翰林方知程輓鱈e世是個無書不讀，無一不會的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個成學。遂向夫人蘇氏說道：“此子日后，必能大振家聲。斷不可以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>庶子待他。”蘇氏夫人答道：“這是不消你說的。”就與程誘蝳P在</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>一個書房里念書。這程誘蝚O哥反受兄弟程輓鱆滷訄V。朝漸夕磨，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一半年間，把程誘蝑蝻楛o也明白了。遂與程輓鬫P年入了邑庠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說這程翰林家，有一件傳家之寶，乃金如意兩枝。前十年時，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>程夫人夜夢一女子，年紀不過十六七歲。進他屋里，拿去金如意一枝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。說道：“程太太，我暫且借去一用，十年以后，定來奉還。”天明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>看時，果然少了一枝。左找右尋，并無蹤影。沒去已久，也不提了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>及至程輓魖生以后。程夫人又在佛前討得一簽。其占云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    玉麟成雙非無緣，如意一支暗引前。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    寶物還家可坐待，何妨借去已多年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>    程夫人把這簽帖拿給程翰林看。程翰林道：“輓魖鄐擐Z成人，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>或者給你復看此物，也未可定。”不提。話說這程輓鰶i學，年只八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>歲。到十歲就補了廩。十二三歲就成了錢塘縣的一個大名士。事親至</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>孝，待兄甚恭。日與程誘蟡S弟兩個，奮志讀書。但家中人提起師弟</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兩字來，他就不覺泣下。說起姊妹兩字來，他便終日嗚咽。父母問其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>緣故，總不肯說。程翰林料其事系前生，以后夫婦二人從此也再不問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>他。馗兒轉生，暫且不提。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知秋英受罪如何？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第十一回  勵堅節受盡百般苦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說馗兒錢塘投生去后，次日撫憲正要提出來再問。忽見獄司走</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來稟道：“監中拘禁的男鬼馗兒，夜間去無蹤影了。”撫院驚訝道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“奇哉，怪哉。有這等義鬼，代為鳴冤。石生的官司，可見是屈了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”遂辦文移會學院，不提。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    再說秋英在蕭判官衙內。一日三次拷打，甚是難當。卻拿定主意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，再不依從。一日蕭判官上城隍衙門里去了，鬼卒們也偷出外邊玩去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了。只落得秋英自己在這里。心中暗惱，不覺啼哭起來。宅內有個小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>使數名喚旋風。閑步到此，見門是鎖著，往里一看，有個少年女子，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>拴在梁頭上，在那里哭哩。心下發悶，便跑到宅中，一五一十，俱對</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>夫人說了。夫人道：“我卻不信。”旋風道：“太太不信，請親去看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>看。是真是假，便見明白。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    夫人跟著旋風出了宅門，走到那屋子前。一看，真是有個女子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>叫鬼卒給我把門開了，鬼卒稟道：“門是判爺封了去的，私自開鎖判</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>爺知道了，小的承當不起。”夫人罵道：“你這該死的奴才，既怕老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>爺獨不怕太太嗎？若不開時，一定重打。”鬼卒無計奈何，只得把門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>開了。夫人進去，又喝道：“把這女子，給我放下來。”這鬼卒又不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>敢不，給他解下梁來。夫人問道：“你這個女子，因何鎖在此處？實</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>說與我知。”秋英稟道：“奴叫秋英，替業師石生鳴冤，來到這里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>判爺不嫌奴丑陋不堪。欲招為二房，奴執意不肯。言語之間，觸怒判</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>爺。把奴拘禁在此，如今已月余了。萬望太太解救。”那夫人把秋英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>細看了一看，夸道：“好個美貌女子，無怪乎那個老貨看中了你。但</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有了你，何以顯我。這個勾當，斷是不准他做的。叫鬼卒偷送你出去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>罷。”秋英叩頭道：“謝過太太。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    鬼卒領著秋英出離了判衙，往東正走。不料與蕭判官兩下里正走</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了個對面。蕭判官問鬼卒道：“你領了這個女鬼上那里去？”鬼卒回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“小的怎敢領他出來，這是太太叫小的領出他來的。”蕭判官道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“胡說，快給我速速領回去。”那鬼卒不敢違拗，把秋英仍送到原</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>舊去處，拴在梁上。蕭判官叫過這個鬼卒來，責他不小心看守，打了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>他二十個板子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    方才退入內宅，夫人一見便發怒道：“你做的好事？”蕭判官道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我有什么不好的事情？”夫人道：“你強逼良家女子為妾，該當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>何罪？我一定上城隍殿前去出首。”判官道：“妻妾之說，人倫所有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。你既不肯容他，我放他走就是了。何必這等發狠。”兩個嚷鬧不住</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。蕭判官見他夫人真是不准，又別處找了一座閑房，離衙門遠遠的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>把秋英鎖在里面。他一日三次，親去看看，叫鬼卒拷打。百般刑罰，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>俱各受過。秋英總不肯半句應承。蕭判官見他志節堅確，從此也漸漸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的松放他了。秋英到這田地，甚是難受。遂作詩一首，以自傷云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    深閨弱女苦形單，漫露花容惹禍端。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    胸矢十年不字志，痛嗟狂奴冒相干。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    空房鎖禁步難轉，終夜哭哀淚眼干。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    形體摧殘半虧損，負仇終須得鳴官。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說春芳在家等候馗兒，几日不見回來。秋英亦渺無音信。又親</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>自□□外邊打聽。才知道秋英還在那里受罪。馗兒已被城隍發往別處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>脫生去了。剩得自己冷冷落落，甚難為情。又念石生在監，近已不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>怎樣。此心一舉，就往黃州獄中去了。卻說石生在監里，正當半夜中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>間。聞一個女子啼哭而來。走至面前，卻是春芳。石生道：“路途遙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>遠，又勞你來看我。”春芳答道：“先生在監，女徒何時敢或置念。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”石生問道：“秋英馗兒為何不同你來呢？”春芳答道：“馗兒往巡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>撫台下告狀，被那處城隍看見，發往錢塘縣脫生去了。秋英往城隍台</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>下告狀，被蕭判官拉去強逼為妾，他執意不從。一日三次拷打，現今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>在那里受罪哩。”石生聽說哭道：“為我一個，倒連累你眾人了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>春芳道：“這原是數該如此，也不瞞怨先生。”遂取出一個布包來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>交給石生說道：“先生的銀子使的將完了。這又是銀子一十五兩，先</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生隨便使用罷。我便這一遭，還不知几時再來看你哩。”遂起身嗚咽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>而去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了次日，禁卒見石生手中，又有了一包銀子。驚異道：“石相</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>公進監時，腰里并無分文。忽然有這銀子二十多兩，并未見人送來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>今又有銀子一包，也沒見是誰來送。莫非有鬼神暗中佑助他不成？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>因留心照料石生，茶是茶，飯是飯。晚間并不拘禁他了。這正是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    善惡到頭終有報，只爭來早與來遲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石生在監里坐著，忽聽得外邊有人傳說：今日官吏人等，俱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>出外接詔去了。心中疑道：“是接的何詔？”晚上禁卒進得監來對石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生道：“今日接的不是憂詔，卻是喜詔。”石生問道：“有何喜詔？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”禁卒道：“天啟皇帝晏駕，崇禎皇帝登基。不日就有大赦。石相公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的官司一定是開釋的了。”石生道：“還恐未必甚穩。”且按下不題</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說崇禎皇爺未登基時，就深惡魏忠賢。到得登基次日，就把魏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>忠賢拿了。剿沒其家，翻出一本賬來。載的俱是些官員，或系他的門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生、或系他的干兒，文武共有二三百人。崇禎皇帝大怒，一概削去其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>職。就有太常卿馬克昌、湖廣學院韓媚、西安府知府范承顏、陝西學</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>院許壽南，一干人在內。又下了一道旨意：凡被魏賊陷害拘禁在獄者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，無論罪之大小，悉行赦宥。旨意已到，黃州府知府把石生立時開出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。用好言安慰，令其回家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生回到羅田，祭掃了墳墓。仍往襄陽而來。一路上，晚行早宿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。聽得人相傳說，魏太監死后，從新又正了法了。許壽南、韓嵋、馬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>克昌、范承顏等，俱流徒出去了。羅田縣知縣錢為黨、長安縣知縣金</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日萃，俱各貶家為民。石生心中暗道：“天道好還，無往不復。所以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>今日有此現報。”行不几程，就到襄陽府了。進的城時，天色已晚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>先到胡員外家，要了鑰匙，好去開門。胡員外一見甚喜。說道：“聞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兄無辜獲罪。今得脫出，可喜可賀。”石生答道：“晚生多蒙老先生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的福力，是以終獲幸免。”又說了几句閑話，拿著鑰匙，開了外門，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>進了書房。已是點燈時候。見春芳站在那里，愁眉不展。石生問道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“馗兒轉生，無容說了。秋英為何，至今還未歸家？”春芳答道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>他還在那判衙里受罪哩。不知几時，才得脫網？”石生怒道：“他既</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>為我受苦，我定替他爭氣。”石生吃了晚飯，向春芳道：“這個劣判</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，殊干天倫。我定上城隍台下，去告他一狀。遂提筆寫一呈道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    具呈黃州府羅田縣廩生石茂蘭，為逼良為妾，乞天究治以正法紀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>事。切照。生身罹刑獄，無由控白。有女徒秋英代生鳴冤台下。不料</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>劣判蕭，漁色為念，拉至衙中，強逼為妾。秋英不允，逐日拷打，性</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>命難保。天條何在？為此上呈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生把呈子寫完，就睡去了。到了次日，早晨起的身來，正是飯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>時。適值胡員外、蔡敬符，對門朱良玉俱來看望。盤桓了片時，又回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>看了一番。天色已晚，只得明早去呈了。誰知石生要代秋英出氣一事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，那蕭判官在衙中早已曉得。一日也無言，到得起更時分。叫鬼卒把</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>秋英領到本衙，解去繩鎖。安慰道：“你這個女子，志同金石，節操</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>冰霜，甚是可敬。但我招你為妾，亦系好意。你既執意不肯，我也斷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不相強。你回去，多多拜上石司馬大人，量能包原。些須小事，不必</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>懷恨在心，放你去罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    秋英幸得脫身，出離了判衙，就直投太平巷來了。石生與春芳在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家點上燈坐著，正說秋英那里受罪，彼此傷嘆。忽聽得外邊角門響了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一聲。春芳抬頭向外一看，不勝驚喜道：“秋英姐姐幸得回家了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>秋英道：“妹妹，我几乎死在那里。”春芳道：“石先生已回家兩天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了。”秋英進得屋中，見了石生，不覺放聲大哭。石生與春芳兩個極</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>力相勸，方才住聲。就把他廟前告狀，被蕭判官拉去的事，詳細說了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一番。石生恨道：“今晚若非放你回來，我斷不與他罷手。”秋英又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“方才我回來時，蕭判官分付的些話，我都曉的。只‘多多拜上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石司馬’這一句，我就不懂了。你是一個秀才，他如何叫做你司馬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>敢問先生這是怎說？”石生答道：“這是個泛常稱呼，別無說處。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石生心中暗忖道：“難道我后日官至司馬不成？”從此師徒們三個，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>情意倍加篤厚。石生讀書愈有興致了。但馗兒投生于他處，他三個人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>提起來，彼此未免有些扼腕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知秋英、春芳二女，后來畢竟如何？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第十二回  度靈魂歷遍萬重山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說翠容小姐在成都府觀音堂內，逐日向佛前焚香拜禮，已經三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>年。就感動了一位羅漢，托夢給他說道：“石家娘子，你的厄期已滿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，石生的魔障將消。須得我去點化一番，好叫你合家完聚。”翠容醒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來卻是一夢。這位羅漢就變做一個行腳僧的模樣，往襄陽府來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    袈裟披身市上行，木魚手敲遠聞聲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    磕頭連把彌陀念，惟化善緣早結成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    這個和尚，日逐在襄陽四關廂里，化那些往來的行客，坐家的鋪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>戶。一日石生偶到城外，見這個和尚化緣。他也上了百文錢的布施。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>那和尚把石生上下一看。問道：“相公貴姓？”石生答道：“賤姓石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”和尚又問道：“尊府住在何處？”石生答道：“住在城里。”和</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>尚道：“我看你滿臉的陰氣，定有陰鬼纏身。”石生答道：“沒有。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”和尚道：“現有兩個女鬼，已與你同居三年。如何瞞得過我？”石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生道：“雖然相伴，卻無害于我。”和尚道：“害是無害，終非人身</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，難成夫婦。待老僧替你度脫一番，試看如何？”就當下畫了一道符</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。上寫兩句咒語：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    聞得哭聲到，便是還陽時。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    和尚遂把這符遞與石生，說道：“你回去，把這符收好。不可叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人看見。到得這月十五日一早。把這道符貼在你外門上。有哭妹子的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過你門前，則此符大有效矣。”石生接過符來，謝了和尚，回到家中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。并不對秋英、春芳說知。這且按下不提。卻說蔡監生的妹子，年已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>十九。他母親給他擇配，大門小戶，總說不妥。忽得了一個暴病而亡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。出殯的日期，正趕到這月十五。一定該石生的書房門口經過。到了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>那一天，這石生黎明起來，把靈符就貼在外門以上。這正是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    妙有點鐵成金手，能使死尸為活人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說蔡家，這一日出殯。正抬著棺材，到了石生書房門首。蔡敬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>符哭了一聲妹子，那棺材忽然落在平地。這石生書房里的秋英，急忙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>跑出門來，一頭鑽入棺材里去了。人人驚訝。來看的，立時就有二三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>百人。只聽得棺材里面喊叫道：“這是個什么去處？悶殺個人。作速</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>放我出去罷！”眾人說：“□□活了，打開看看，也是無妨的。”蔡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>監生攔阻不住，抬去了棺罩。打開材蓋，只見蔡監生的妹子突然起來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>坐著。蔡監生向前問道：“妹子你好了？”他妹子說道：“我不是你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>妹子，我并沒有個哥哥，你是何人？冒來認我。”說完就跳出棺來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>直向石生書房里邊去了。蔡監生正要拉住，倒被他罵了几句。說道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“我只認得石生，你與我何親何故？竟敢大膽，強來相拉。”蔡監生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>見不認他，也無奈何。只得叫人把空棺抬到別處，自往家中告訴他母</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>親去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生知道是蔡監生的妹子，不好出來直看。偷眼一覷，真是一位</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>絕色的佳人。眉眼身材，無一處不與秋英一般。這個女子，連聲叫道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“石先生那里去了？”石生卻再不好出來。說話中間，蔡監生的母</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>親，走來相認。女子道：“我母親去世早了，只有一個表妹子，在此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>與我作伴。同跟著石先生念書。你是誰家的老媽？強來給我做娘。東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>院里胡太太，才是我的娘哩。”蔡監生母親知是借尸還魂，難以強認</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了。大哭一場，轉身回去。胡員外聽說，叫他夫人過來。把這女子，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>接到家中，認為義女。與蔡監生商議，各備妝奩一付，送過來與石茂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>蘭擇吉拜堂成親。那洞房中夫妻恩愛，也不必細說。卻說石生與秋英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>成親以后，每日晚間再也不見春芳的形跡了。忽一夜間石生夫婦二人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，忽聽得窗外有人說道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    本是同林鳥，遷喬獨早鳴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    羨爾長比翼，何靳呼群聲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    說罷，繼之以哭。秋英道：“這是春芳妹子，瞞怨我哩。”相公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>何不再求那位老僧也度脫他一番。”石生道：“我明日就去，但不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這個和尚走了沒走？”到了次日，石生出城一看，那個和尚還在那里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>化緣哩。石生向前致謝道：“多蒙禪師的法力，秋英已借尸還魂，轉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>成人身了。”和尚問道：“你今又來做什么？”石生答道：“還有春</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>芳未轉人身，再求老禪師度脫則個。”和尚道：“度脫靈魂，自是好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>事。但湊合難以盡巧，這只要看他的造化何如？你回去打整一座靜屋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，里外俱要糊的嚴密。明日晚上，在家中候我罷。”石生回家與秋英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>說了，遂打掃一座淨屋，糊得嚴絲合縫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了次日，掌燈以后。那個化緣的和尚，果然到了。向石生道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“我進屋里去，外邊把門給我鎖了。住七日七夜，我里邊叫開門時，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>方准你來開。我若不叫，斷不可私自開門。”石生悉依其言，等的到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了第七日，天將黑時，并無半點動靜。秋英道：“這個和尚，未必不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是遁了。你何不偷去看看。”石生走到窗前，用舌尖舐破了一個小孔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。向里一張，只見那和尚兩眼緊閉，盤膝打坐。就像個死人一般。石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生恐怕驚醒了他，當時把小孔糊煞。回來向秋英道：“走是沒走，還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>無音信哩。”知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    又住了半頓飯時，忽見從外走來一個女子。身材細長，頭腳嚴緊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。容色與春芳相似，止好有十七八歲。慌忙跑到屋里，一頭倒在床上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，似死非死，似睡非睡。唬的秋英躲在一旁站著。外邊那和尚連聲叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“快來開門，快來開門。”石生出去把門開開，和尚下的床來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>說道：“跑煞我，跑煞我。我為你這一位室人，經過了千山萬水。方</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>才做的這般妥當。我還得同你到屋里看看去。”石生就領著這個和尚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>走到屋里。只見春芳從那屋角里鑽出，這和尚過去，一把揪到床前，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>往那女子身上一推，就不見春芳的蹤影了。那女子口中叫道：“姐姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>我好腳疼。”睜開眼看著秋英道：“我沒上那里去？我身上乏困，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>像走了几千里路的一般。”秋英道：“妹妹你歇息兩天便精神了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這外邊的和尚遂立時執意要走。石生極力相留，再留不住。說道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>異日登高眺遠，你我定有相逢之期。實不能在此久留。”送出門來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>并不知向那里去了。石生進得房中一看，這個女子畢真就是春芳分毫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不差。胡員外遂又叫他夫人過來，把這女子領去，收為義女。治辦妝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>奩，擇了吉期，以便過門。卻說到了過門之時，蔡監生的母親合對門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>朱夫人，俱來送飯。朱夫人一見新人便異樣道：“這分明是王小姐，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>如何來到這里？”心下游疑，也不敢認真。是夕客散之后，春芳與石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生成為夫婦。三人共作詩一首云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    淑女歷來稱好逑（蘭），懷春何必分明幽（英）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    絲羅共結由天定（芳），琴瑟永偕豈人謀（蘭）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    荒草塚前骨已掩（蘭），芸經堂內魂猶留（英）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    赤繩系足割難斷（芳），聊借別軀樂同ヤ（蘭）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石生既有了室家，又得胡員外的幫助，心中甚是寬舒。留心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>討朱裴文的指教，到了八月秋闈就與朱良玉、蔡敬符三個合伴赴省應</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>試。及至揭曉石茂蘭中了解元，朱■中了第十一名舉人，蔡寅中了副</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>榜。到得來春會試，朱■不第先回。石茂蘭中了第八名進士，在京中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>多住了月余。有廣東一位新進士，姓王名灼字其華。聞石生將回襄陽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，找來與石生搭伴，說道：“襄陽府有弟的一位年伯，欲去探望探望</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。要與年兄同船，不知肯相容否？”石生答道：“如此正妙，但不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>貴年誼是那一家？”王其華答道：“是太平巷內胡涵齋。”石生道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“那是家岳。”王進士道：“這樣說來，更加親熱了。”兩個同船，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來到襄陽。石生回家，王進士直往胡宅去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    一日，石生請王進士赴席。約胡員外、蔡敬符、朱良玉奉陪。蔡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>寅先到胡宅與王進士說話，好以便同來。說起秋英還魂一事，王進士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“世間竟有這樣奇事？”剛才說完，石生那邊就著人來請。胡員</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>外道：“老夫有事，不能奉陪。敬符兄陪了王世兄過去罷。”蔡寅陪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>著王進士，到得石生家。朱良玉早已過來相候。王進士原與朱良玉系</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>結拜的兄弟，相見已畢，彼此敘了些家常。坐著正說話時，適石生廚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>下缺少家伙，春芳向鄰家去借。王進士看見春芳，隨后跟出門來，□</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>地一眼。春芳紅了紅臉，急三步走到鄰家去了。借了几件家伙走出門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>時，王進士還在街上站著看哩。一眼覷定春芳，直看的他走入院里去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，方才回頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    春芳到了家里，放下家伙，向石生道：“你請的這個同年，卻不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是個好人，方才我去借家伙，他不住的左一眼，右一眼看了我個勾數</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。他是胡娘家的年誼，究非親姊熱妹，如何這般不分男女？”石生道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“既是年誼，就不相拘，你莫要怪他。”石生出來，正要讓坐。王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>進士道：“年兄不必過急，弟還有一句要緊話相懇。”石生道：“年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兄有何見教？”王進士道：“年兄你既系胡年伯家的嬌客，你我就不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>啻郎舅。方才出來的這位年嫂，是胡年伯從小養成的？還是外邊走來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的？”石生答道：“卻是從外邊走來的。”王進士道：“既是這樣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一定要請出來作揖。仔細看看，以釋弟惑。”石生道：“就是兩個俱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>看看何妨？”石生與蔡寅陪著王進士走到院中。石生叫道：“你兩個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>俱出來，王年兄請作揖哩。”秋英整身而出與王進士見禮讓坐。蔡寅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>指著秋英向王進士道：“這就是舍妹，借尸還魂在此。”左右叫春芳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，再不肯出來。秋英進入里間，勉強推出。方才與王進士見禮。見過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>禮仍轉入里間去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    王進士仔細看了一番，不覺泣下。石生道：“這是為何？”王進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>士道：“年兄有所不知，前歲三四月間，舍妹促亡，尸首被風撮去，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>并沒處找尋。方才門口看見這位年嫂，還不敢認得十分真切。今對面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一看，的是舍妹無疑了。但不知是何時來到這里？”石生答道：“就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是年前四月間走來的。”王進士哭道：“這分明也是借尸還魂了。如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>何還肯認我？”秋英道：“王家哥哥，不必悲痛。你看我待蔡家哥哥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>如何？就叫他也跟我一樣罷了。”秋英叫春芳出來，仍拜王進士為兄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。方才大家到了前廳，坐席。席終而散。朱夫人見是王小姐借尸還魂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，仍舊認為義女。不時的來接去。這王進士在胡員外家住了月余，臨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>起身回家時，又到石生家里來看春芳。說道：“妹子路途遙遠，委實</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不便接你。但愿妹丈選到廣州左近，姊妹見面，庶可不難了。”春芳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“這是哥哥屬望的好意，只恐妹子未必有這樣造化。”王進士又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>與石生、朱良玉、蔡敬符盤桓了一天。次日就起身往廣東走了。從此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石茂蘭、胡員外、朱良玉、蔡敬符四姓人家，俱成親戚你往我來，逐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日不斷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知房翠容小姐與石生后來如何見面？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第十三回  觀音寺夫妻重聚面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說石生自發身之后，一年捷取，就放了南陽府的刑廳。三年俸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>滿，轉升了四川成都府的知府。到任兩月，秋英春芳二位夫人因路上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>經了些險阻，許下在觀音堂還愿。先差衙役來對廟中老尼說知。那老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>尼就打掃了殿宇，預備下茶果。分付翠容道：“聞說這兩位太太，俱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>系妙年。我年邁耳沉，應答恐不利便。一會來時，我只在神前伺候。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一切照應，俱托付給你罷。”翠容應過。住不多時，衙役進來說道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“太太的轎已到山門口了。師傅們速出去迎接迎接。”翠容聽說整容</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>而出。兩位夫人已經下轎。翠容向前稟道：“小尼失誤遠迎，乞太太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>見諒。”秋英答道：“俺特來還愿，還要仗托師傅的法力。如何怪你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”翠容陪著兩位太太，先到了佛前拜過。然后到觀音殿內上了香燭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。發了錢箔。老尼誦平安經一卷。兩位太太方才磕頭起來。向老尼謝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“有勞師傅祝贊。”老尼答道：“太太到此，理應伺候。但老尼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>年邁耳沉，叫小徒陪太太禪堂里吃茶罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    翠容陪兩位太太，到了禪堂里坐下。把茶果獻上，自己卻在下面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>站著相陪。秋英心中打量，暗忖道：“看這個尼姑舉動有些官樣大方</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，分明是個宦家的氣象。如何落在廟中？”因問道：“師傅貴庚几何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了？”翠容答道：“虛度三十歲了。”秋英太太又問道：“你是從小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>出家的，還是半路里修行的？”翠容答道：“是半路投來的。”秋英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>又問道：“你系何處人？為什么來到這里？”翠容道：“說起來話長</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，恐二位太太厭聽。”秋英道：“這卻無妨，你說俺才明白哩。”翠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>容道：“小尼是黃州府羅田縣人氏。”秋英又問道：“你曾有丈夫嗎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>？”翠容道：“有。”秋英道：“姓甚名誰，是什么人家？”翠容答</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“拙夫姓石名茂蘭，是個廩生。公公石峻峰，系兩榜出身，做過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>長安縣知縣。后升廣西柳州府的知府。”秋英太太便道：“這等說來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，你真是個宦家的娘子了。失敬失敬。”就讓他在旁邊里坐下。春芳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>聽見提起石茂蘭三字，心中詫異。兩眼不住的向秋英盡覷，秋英只當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不睬。又問道：“你為何一個女流就來到這里？”翠容答道：“公婆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不幸早逝，后被奸人陷害。因公公在長安居官時，有河一道失誤挑修</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。文提石郎變產修河，一去二年并無音信。后有長安縣的關移說石郎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>已經病故了。對門有個王詮，要娶小尼為妾。暗地著人，把小尼的母</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>親治死。小尼欲報母仇，因假為應承。幸有觀音老母，賜給神藥一包</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，名為催命丹。及至到了他家，把這藥向那人面上洒去，那人就立時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>死了。小尼那時正要逃走，忽被一陣狂風，刮到這里。因此修行，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>能回家，已數年了。”這正是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    訴盡從前艱苦事，漸啟后來亨通緣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    秋英太太道：“你丈夫姓石，我家老爺也姓石。你是黃州羅田縣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人，我家老爺雖居襄陽，原籍也是黃州羅田縣人。你丈夫既然是個秀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>才，說起來我家老爺未必不認的他。回去向我家老爺說知，如有人上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>羅田縣去，叫他把你丈夫或存或沒，再打聽個的確。設法送你回籍如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>何？”翠容謝道：“多蒙二位太太垂憐。”兩位夫人各送了二兩銀子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的香資。翠容送出山門，上轎而去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    兩位夫人回到內宅。秋英向春芳道：“今日在廟中見的這個尼姑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，定是翠容姐姐無疑了。”春芳道：“若不是他，如何知得這般清楚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”晚間石生歸房問道：“你兩個還過愿了。”秋英答道：“愿是還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過了，俺卻見了一樁異事。”石生問道：“什么異事？”秋英道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>今日廟中，見了一個連毛的尼姑。年紀不過三十。問其來歷，他丈夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的姓名籍貫卻與相公一般。你說前妻翠容姐不知死在何處？據今日看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來，還是活在這里哩。何不速去接來，以圖完聚。”石生沉吟道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>接是不難，恐未必的確。尤不可造次，下官職到黃堂，屬下有多少官</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>員，城中有多少紳衿。突然認一尼姑為妻，恐惹人恥笑。”秋英答道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“相公差矣，夫婦一倫，本諸性天。避小嫌，而忘大倫，何以為人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。公祖統馭萬民，不認斷使不的。你若是信不真，明日權當齋僧，親</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去一看。如果然不錯，就接來罷了。”石生依允。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了次日，石生率領人役，往觀音堂內齋僧。進的廟來，先參拜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了佛像。驚異道：“這尊佛像，好與襄陽化緣的老僧相似。轉入后殿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>行禮已畢，走到公案前坐下。把廟中几個尼姑叫出來從頭點名。點到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>翠容跟前，石生一看，果然是他前妻房翠容。翠容一見石生，明認的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是他的丈夫，卻不敢相認。石生問道：“夜日太太回宅，說有一個出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家的尼姑，系黃州府羅田縣人。就是你嗎？”翠容答道：“正是小尼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”石生道：“現今有本府的一個親戚姓吳。他是羅田縣城里人，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>久他的家眷回家。本府接你到我衙中，叫他攜帶你同船回去。你意下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>如何？”翠容謝道：“多蒙太老爺的恩典。”石生齋僧已過，回到宅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>中。對秋英、春芳說道：“果然是我前妻房翠容。我已許下，明日去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>接他。”秋英道：“如此才是。”石生道：“但恐來到，有些不妥，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>叫下官卻作難了。”秋英道：“天下原有定禮，妾雖無知，頗曉得個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>尊卑上下。接來時，自能使彼此相安。相公無容多慮。”閑言提過。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了次日，石生適值撫台提進省去。秋英便著人役，打著全付執</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>事，抬著四人大轎。差了兩個管家婆去接翠容太太。他與春芳姊妹二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人，卻在宅內整容相候。及至接回來，轎到宅門，翠容方才下轎。秋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>英、春芳兩個向前緊走几步，伏身稟道：“賤妾秋英春芳，迎接太太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”翠容連忙上前，兩手拉住。說道：“奴乃出家賤尼，石郎還未知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>肯相認否？二位太太，如何這等恭敬。”秋英道：“妾等已與老爺說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>明，那有不認之理。但老爺適值進省，妾等先把太太接進宅來。俟老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>爺回署，好合家完聚。”就把翠容讓到中堂，延之上座。地下鋪上氈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>條。秋英春芳兩個轉下，并肩而立。讓道：“太太請上，受妾等一拜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”房翠容回禮道：“奴家也有一拜。”彼此拜禮已畢。翠容向秋英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>春芳道：“奴家若非二位妹子引進，何由得見天日，嗣后只以姊妹相</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>稱，切莫拘嫡庶形跡。使我心下不安。”秋英道：“尊卑自有定分，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>何敢差越。”三個從此，彼此相敬相愛。轉眼間，不覺數日了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生自省回署，進得后宅，秋英迎著說道：“房氏太太已經接來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>數日了。老爺進來相認罷。”石生見了翠容抱頭大哭，秋英春芳在傍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>亦為落淚。翠容向石生道：“你為何捎書叫我改嫁？”石生道：“書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是假的。”翠容又道：“長安縣的來文，說你已經死了。”石生道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“文也是旁人做的。”石生問翠容道：“怎么你能來到這里？”翠容</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>把從前情由，自始至終，說給石生聽了。石生也把秋英春芳配合的情</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>由，也說給他聽。翠容道：“我只說這兩位妹子是你另娶的，卻不料</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>世間竟有這等出奇的姻緣。”石生向翠容道：“你為我受盡折磨，他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兩個的靈魂與我同過患難，情意一也。大小之分，任憑夫人所命罷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”翠容說道：“妾雖妄居□□，幸得離而復合，吾愿足矣。嗣后家中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一切大小事務，俱叫他兩個執掌。俺總以姊妹相處，講什么大小嫡庶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”石生道：“夫人既能這樣，日后下官定請三付冠誥，封贈爾等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    翠容又向石生道：“妾在患難之時，曾蒙菩薩點化，到得此處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>又多承老尼照理。曾許下團圓后，重修廟宇，酬謝師恩。望相公先領</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>妾去參拜一番。不知准否？”石生應允。著衙役先去向廟中老尼說知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。衙役回來稟道：“觀音寺只剩得一座中殿，兩邊廊房、前面的佛殿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>、后面的禪堂俱成空地。連老尼也走去杳無蹤影了。”翠容方知這老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>尼就是菩薩變成的。佛殿禪堂俱是菩薩布置的虛景。遂叫人重修廟宇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。不題。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生一日在衙中無事，與三位夫人坐著閑談。庭前有老槐一株，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石生以此為題。叫三位夫人聯句，作詩一首。石生先詠道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    回憶當年徒奔波（蘭），古槐影下堪婆娑（翠）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    勁枝雖被春光早（英），柔條還沾雨露多（芳）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    綠作復云葉茂密（蘭），黃應秋日氣沖和（翠）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    勢成連理有緣定（英），何必誦詩慕伐柯（芳）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    又一日，石生登峨眉山。到了山上，往下一看，形勢崇高，如在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>半虛空中。又向四下里一望，但見層巒疊峰，袤延八百余里。石生一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>時興發，遂拈筆題詩一首道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    懸崖萬丈梯難升，峭壁轉回須攀藤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>    一帶連岡形險隉A兩峰對峙不騫崩。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    白龍日繞池中躍，夜晚遙望放錦燈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>    四蜀固多叢繭處，此較劍閣尤■Ъ。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    題詩已完，往前走到一座古剎前，名叫華林禪院。意欲進去一看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，和尚聽說，打掃了一座干淨禪室。把石生迎到里邊去。經過大殿山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>頭旁，有一個小角門。忽聞一陣異香，從中吹出。石生到禪室里坐定</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，問和尚道：“你前邊小門里鎖的房子，盛著什么東西，氣味如此馨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>香。”和尚稟道：“無甚東西，內有一座禪堂。相傳百余年前，有一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>位老師傅坐化到里面，至今并未葬他。里外門俱是他親自叫人鎖的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>說下不准人開。這些年來，也沒人敢動。又相傳這位師傅已經成佛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>常與觀音老母虛設法象，點化愚人。留下四句禪語，并無人解得。石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生道：“取來我看。”和尚從柜中，取出一個紅紙帖來，遞與石生。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>拆開一看，上寫道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    似我非真我，見我才是我，煩我曾留我，遇我豈負我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生暗想道：“這莫不是襄陽化緣的老僧嗎？”叫和尚開了角門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，進里一看。見禪堂門上，貼著一道封皮。上寫著“門待有緣開”五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個字。揭去封皮，開了房門。當門一張大床，床上有一位坐化的老僧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。渾身盡是塵土，背后貼著個紙條。寫著道：“坐化人即是化緣人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”叫人掃去土塵，仔細一看，就是那化緣的老僧，面貌如生。石生拜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“此乃羅漢點化我也。”下了山來，就命人立時重修殿宇。把坐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>化的老僧妝塑金身，送在里面，焚香供養。石生一家團聚不題。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    不知馗兒轉生還能相見否？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第十四回  藩司衙師徒再談心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石生在成都，做知府三年。轉升了四川糧道，做道三載。屢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有奇績，選遷了浙江的布政。是時馗兒，已轉生十三歲了。石生到任</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>，簿書之暇，行文觀風。取的錢塘縣首卷就是程輓驉C石生喜其寫作</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>俱佳，賞賜的甚是優厚。一日程輓魖蚆藏縞x。石生聞其年幼，有些</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>羨慕。請到內書房里相會。程輓鰶i得書房，向石生行禮已畢，石生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>讓他坐下，著人獻茶。石生上下打量，宛然是馗兒的模樣。開口問道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>：“賢契青春几何？”程輓鰽疚D：“生員虛度十三歲了。”石生又</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>問道：“入泮几年？”程輓鰽疚D：“僥幸五載了。”石生又問道：</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“賢契如此妙年，佳章居然老手，可是宿構，卻出新裁呢？”程輓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>答道：“生員雖拙于作文，然深恥抄錄。”石生道：“文章既系盡出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>心裁，異日所造，應難相量。賢契的先生果是何人？”程輓鰽疚D：</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“生員幸承庭訓，并未曾投師。”石生聽其言談，又畢真像馗兒的聲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>口。心中愈發驚異。程輓鰷茯搘菪籵拑M是昔日的光景。但身系轉生</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，難以遽認。程輓鬫]說道：“生員年幼無知，陡膽冒瀆，敢問大人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>籍貫何處？”石生答道：“本司原籍黃州，寄居襄陽。”程輓髐S問</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>道：“住在襄陽那街？”石生答道：“住在太平巷內。”程輓髐S問</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“太平巷有個胡員外，大人可曾認識他嗎？”石生答道：“此人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>本司的岳丈，賢契你如何知得這般清楚？”程輓鰽疚D：“胡員外與</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家君曾在京中同寓，是以知其端底。”隨即又問道：“胡員外有閑宅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一處，里面住著一位石先生，大人可曾會過嗎？”石生見程輓鬙y句</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道著自己，便答道：“此人本司卻合他甚熟。”就轉問道：“我部他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有個徒弟名喚馗兒，后來轉生錢塘，不知歸落誰家了？”說到此處，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>程輓鱈K不得不認，□道：“大人莫非就是九畹石先生嗎？”石生道</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>：“你莫非就是馗兒所轉的嗎？前世之事還記得否？”程輓鰽疚D：</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“月下賦詩，當堂質訟，為時几何？竟至忘記耶？門生今日，幸得再</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>見先生。但不知二位姐姐，還在彼處否？”石生答道：“他兩個已轉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>成人身，與本司結成夫婦了。”程輓鷞D：“門生雖系轉世，兩位夫</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人意欲還求一見，不知肯相容否？”石生道：“那有不容之理，但須</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>本司先為說明，以便請你進去。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生說罷，轉入內宅。春芳便問道：“聽說老爺外邊會客，不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>會的何客？”石生答道：“下官觀風，取中了錢塘的一個廩生，年紀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>才十三歲。今日特來謝我，下官仔細盤問，方知他就是馗兒所轉。問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>到你姊妹二人，他還要求見一面，不知該怎么樣？”秋英說道：“既</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>是這般，就該請進來一會才是。”石生便著家人，把程輓鷜苳J內宅</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。秋英、春芳兩位夫人，早在檐下相候。三個見面，彼此落淚。春芳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>道：“兄弟你轉生才几年，就長的怎模大了。”程輓鷞D：“弟已系</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>轉世為人，不料與二位姐姐，尚能相會一面。”秋英道：“這是數該</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>如此，你我焉能作主。”秋英春芳領著程輓鬫}參見了翠容夫人。程</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>輓鰲N要告辭。石生道：“今日這樣奇逢，那有遽去之理。”就在內</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>宅里設席款待程輓驉C石生作詩一首，相夸道：</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    聚首一堂尚可提，校書燈下仿青□，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    形骸雖變元神在，素□依然一木雞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    程輓髐]作詩一首，相和道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    天形下覆如張弓，世事百年一夢中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    桃李公門猶在列，前緣寧敢付東風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    席終以后，春芳向石生道：“昔年馗兒上學，曾以金如意為許，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>老爺今日還他的罷。”石生道：“正該還他。”秋英道：“我收著哩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>。”立時取出，交與程輓驉C春芳道：“這是你程家傳世之寶，你前</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>世上學時，無以為贄，我暗與程太夫人借用。許下十年以后，定去還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>他。今日帶去，務要交個清楚。”說完程輓鷖蒢瞼菪穻蚋k。到了家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>中，程翰林與夫人問道：“你為何在衙門里就住了一天。”程輓鰽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“石大人見孩兒年輕，甚是喜歡。設席款待，所以未能早回。三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>位太太俱准我見。孩兒臨來時，三太太給了一件寶物。叫我回家交給</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>母親。”夫人道：“是何寶物？”程輓鰼q袖中，取出一個紙包，遞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>與夫人。展開一看，卻是金如意一枝。夫人大驚道：“奇怪，奇怪，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這金如意是咱家傳世之寶。十數年前，夢一女子借去。左右找尋，并</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>無蹤影。生你之后，討得一簽，說此物不久還家。今日果然原物還來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。但不知這枝如意，緣何落到石太太手中。我將來一定要問個明白。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”這且不提。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石生得了程輓鰴o個門生，雖系新交，實屬故人。不時的請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>到衙門里來敘談。是時正當春月，天氣清朗，人煙和煦。石生向程</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>覃道：“聞得天台山，雁蕩系貴省的名山。同賢契一游何如？”程</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>覃答道：“大人既肯屈駕，門生理應奉陪。”石生于是揀了一個良辰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。帶得程輓鰹|往天台山去。上的山來，一看，真正是奇峰插天，長</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>溪繞地，名秀之致。與別山大不相同。石生道：“勝地不可空游。你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>我須各人賦詩一首，以志登賞。石生遂口詠一詩道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    □茨遺蹤不復留，石梁勝景猶堪游。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    飛峰壁立可回雁，激湍奔騰似龍湫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    華頂寵從勝熊耳，玉宵鑿秀喻牛頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    桃花洞遠無人到，誤入至今傳阮劉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    程輓髐]口詠一詩道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    曇華亭跡至今留，騷客梯岩時一游。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    玉閣參差堪宿雁，瑤樓層轉鎖靈湫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    碧林風動震人耳，瑤草繽紛滿嶺頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    寒拾二仙足嘗到，一方蒙佑免虔劉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    吟詠已畢。石生夸道：“賢契此詩，可謂英年之作，倍勝老成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>”程答輓鷞D：“門生在大人面前，不揣固陋，何異雷門擊鼓。”山</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>上有一座古廟，名為天台神觀。觀內有道士，聽說藩台大人上山，觀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>內打整的甚是干淨。就請到里面獻茶。石生說道：“此山佳景甚多，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一時難以遍覽。不知別處還有古跡嗎？”道士稟道：“小觀東南里半</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>許，有太白金星的行宮。廟門前有石碑一統，上面有長就的律詩一首</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，風吹日晒，多少年來，字書總不磨滅。這卻是此處的一景。大人請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>屈駕一覽。”石生聽說，遂同程輓鷒簼w道士，出了觀門，直上東南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>而去。走不多時到了廟前，見山門上挂著“太白金星行宮”六個大字</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的一面豎匾。門前果然有一統碑，碑上的詩句，真如長就的一般。卻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>又甚是□亮。石生向前讀其詩道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    時運亨通不厭遲，兩陰相助尤為奇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    天台雖異賢孝坊，須憶當年相面時。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生念完了詩句，恍然大悟。才知道曹半仙是太白金星變成的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>并非俗人。遂進到廟中，禮拜了。游玩一會，石生遂下了山。回入衙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>中，向三位夫人說知此事。秋英說道：“太白金星既這樣的點化老爺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，老爺不可不仰答神庥。”遂立時把廟宇蓋的煥然一新。這且不題。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>    再說程輓驉A那日同石生上了天台，回到家中，把石生上山的事</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>情，一一告訴他父親程翰林。說道：“石大人乃當代文人，一生卻有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這些異事。”蘇氏夫人遂接口道：“咱的金如意，多年不見，忽然還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家。難道就不是一樁異事嗎？恨我不能親見石太太，問個詳細。終叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>我心里發悶。”程翰林道：“這也不難，輓魖酮J是石大人的門生，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>便與石大人即系通家兄弟般。就彼此來往，也是無妨的。明日下三個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>請帖，請三位太太過來赴席。你當面問他，便見分曉。次日，程夫人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>果下啟來請。秋英稟知石生。石生道：“門生家不同別人，去也無妨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了那日，程夫人又著人速請了三次。這三位太太盛飾儀容，午</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>間乘轎過去。到得程宅門首，才落轎時。程夫人早出二門來迎。三位</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>太太，走入內宅。程夫人看這三位太太，真真是個個俊如天仙。又仔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>細把春芳太太端相，卻與當年夢中所見的女子一般。又與程輓鱆滲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>情相彷，心下更加疑悶。讓入中堂，相見敘禮讓坐獻茶已畢。說話之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>間，程夫人漸漸言及金如意一事。秋英太太說道：“今日蒙程太太厚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>愛，正該彼此談笑。從前已過之事，莫須深究。”程夫人轉問春芳，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>春芳總是笑而不言。席終以后，程夫人把翠容太太讓到別處，再三的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>根問。翠容太太，方把秋英春芳借尸還魂并馗兒投生錢塘的事，一一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>說了一番。程夫人才知道程輓鷋P秋英春芳原系前世姊妹，合石大人</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>原系師生。平日提起師徒、姊妹四字，程輓髐ㄢ虓[戚，正是為的這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個緣故。自此以后，程夫人與石大人家三位太太，彼此往來不絕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知石生在浙江后來做官如何？再看下文分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第十五回  狼虎店義仆救主難</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說石生做浙江布政，適值代理按察事務。滁州地方有一座老山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，山上多洞，洞中聚集有兩三千人，欲謀不軌。地方官秘秘報知巡撫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，巡撫與石生商議。石生道：“事系風聞，未見確據。不可冒為題奏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，亦不可輕行剿沒。必須打聽個真實，方可相機行事。”巡撫道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>就煩貴司前示私訪一番，回來再作計較。”石生依允。回衙只得換上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>便服，帶了一個茶房。妝作算卦的模樣，出了省城。一路私訪前去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不多些時，到了滁州地方。日逐在鎮店上賣卜。忽有一個賊眉賊眼的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，上來算卦。石生觀其氣象，分明是個反叛。那人問道：“先生是子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>平，是六壬？”石生答道：“兩件都會。”那人道：“既是兩件都會</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，我一定算算。但此處不甚僻靜，你跟我到家里算上一天。如果算的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>好，封資情愿加倍奉送。”石生答道：“我就跟你去。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    那人把石生領到一座山上，進入洞中。同伙的問道：“這是何人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>？”那人答道：“是個六壬先生。”又指茶房問道：“這系先生的何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人？”石生答道：“這是小徒。”石生偷眼一覷，見刀槍旗幟，無不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>俱備。真真是謀反無疑了。石生問道：“既要算命，請寫出貴造來一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>看。”那人說道：“實不瞞你，俺們要舉行大事。特請先生來，給俺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>擇一個興兵的日期。以便起手。”石生把六壬書展開一看說道：“這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>三個月以前，并無興兵的日期。必須過這三個月以后，方好。現今是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>四月盡間，過了五六七三個月，到得八月十六，是個黃道吉辰。下山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>定獲全勝。”那人道：“俺也看著必到那時才好。”方才算完要走，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>那人道：“先生既到我山中，有來的路，沒去的路。洞中正缺少一個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>軍師，俺就拜你做個軍師罷。若要強回去，殊覺不便。”石生恐喪性</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>命，只得假為依從。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了次日，山中筑起一壇。叫石生登在壇上，眾賊羅拜于下。那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>些賊人認真石生住下，自此以后，任所指揮，無不奉命。住有十數多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>天，一日天氣清明，眾賊齊下山去打獵。只剩得石生、茶房二人在洞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>中看守。石生分付茶房道：“你看看這些賊人下山是往那里去，即來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>稟我。”茶房出去一看，見洞中兩三千人，張弓挾矢，牽狗架鷹，下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>山俱往西南一路去了。茶房速進洞，稟知石生。石生道：“咱訪查已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>真，還不速走，更待何時。”茶房遂扶著石生下山，往東北而去。這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石生一路走著，遂口詠古風一首，單單自道其苦云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    山勢■岩石徑斜，草木叢冗亂如麻。窮■絕鳥難投步，左盼右顧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>堪咨嗟。嗟私行太伶仃，倉皇誤入險陂中。萬丈崇嶺藏虎豹，千層深</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>洞伏蛇龍。君不見，白云籠罩影縹緲，紅日照射色暗淡。子規聲叫高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>樹頭，孤猿哀啼長溪岸。一路行來多崎嶇，氣竭力盡肝腸斷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石生怕賊人追趕，走的甚是忙迫。直走到紅日西沉，并未住</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>腳。忽然山上跑下來一只猛虎，把茶房一爪叨去。嚇得石生魂不附體</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，半日心神方定。往前又走，天色漸黑，見一個樵夫擔著一擔山柴，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>從旁而過。石生問道：“前面何處有店？”樵夫答道：“前去三十五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里，方才有店。左近是沒有的。”石生甚是擔憂，黑影里又走了五七</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>里路。抬頭一看，遠遠望見山坡下有一道火光，像個庄村的模樣。就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>望著那火光投去。到了跟前，卻是一個小獨庄。外邊門戶高大，里面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>樓閣層層。石生把門一敲，內有十四五歲的一個幼童開門問道：“是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>做什么的？”石生道：“是借宿的。”幼童道：“相公少待，我去稟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>知主母，再回你信。”住了一會，出來說道：“主母已知，請相公客</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>舍里坐。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生進到客位里面，見燈燭燦列，擺設齊整。從背靠后轉出一位</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>少年婦人，花容艷妝，緩步來前。與石生見了禮。分賓主坐下。向石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生問道：“相公從何處而來？”石生答道：“在下姓梁，往山中治買</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>木料。下山過晚，趕店不及，欲借貴舍暫宿一宵。”婦人答道：“房</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子盡有，但恐屈駕。”石生問道：“娘子尊姓？”婦人答道：“賤妾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>姓薛，拙夫叫薛呈瑞。是個茶商，往山東登州府貿易，去已數年，并</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>無信息。落得妾身，煢煢無依，甚是淒涼。相公適投寒舍，這是前世</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有緣了。”遂命人收拾桌張，讓石生上座，自己在旁相陪。美酒佳肴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，登時陳上。叫出兩個頭發眉齊的女童，在桌子以前歌舞，舞的甚是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>好看。只聽得口歌古風一章道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    野有蔓草兮，零零壤壤。有美一人兮，宛如清陽。邂逅相遇兮，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>與子潛藏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    歌罷，石生看那婦女，甚是風流。不覺的引動了春心。席終，兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>個同入臥室。觀其床帳、器皿，并非尋常人家所有。是夜，石生與那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>女子同枕共寢。到雞將叫時，那女子向石生道：“此處非君久戀之所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，天色漸明，作速起來出去罷。”石生起的身來，還有些留戀之意。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兩個女童，前面拉著。這個女子后邊推著，把石生一直送出門外，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>把大門緊緊關上，再叫也無人答應了。石生甚是漠然，往前走不多時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，回頭看時，卻是一塚大墳。墳前以上，寫著宋貴妃卞氏之墓。石生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>嘆道：“吾幸得該入桃源，寧復許后人問津耶。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    往前走到日夕，落到一個店中。院子甚深，房子甚稠。石生進來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>揀了一間干淨小屋住下。到了掌燈已后，忽有一個賣絨線的，背著包</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>袱進店來投宿。店主道：“別無閑房，只有半間草屋，你將就著住一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>夜罷。”這人就進屋去睡了。石生那知道這是賊店，約有半更天時，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>也就放心睡去。到得夜靜眾賊齊出，把別房里住的几個行客，俱經害</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>訖。后到石生屋中，石生正在夢中，這賊上去，用繩緊緊捆住。石生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>方醒來，求道：“我與你無仇，行李內還有三五十兩銀子，任你拿去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，饒我的性命罷。”那賊道：“銀子是要拿的，這個餛飩湯你也是要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>吃了。”那一個賊道：“夜未甚深，江上打漁的還未散盡，俟四更后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>送他去未遲。”眾賊拿了銀子，仍轉回院內。卻把個草屋里賣絨線的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>忘下了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生身上捆的難受，口中長嘆道：“我石茂蘭不料死在此處。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>那賣絨線的聽見，心中暗道：“這莫不是我故主嗎？”起身出來，走</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>到窗前。小聲問道：“□客，方才說你姓名，你是那里人？”石生答</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“我是黃州府羅田縣永寧街上人。”賣絨線的道：“這樣說起來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，分明是我家大爺了。”石生問道：“你系何人？”賣絨線的道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>我是來喜。”石生道：“你快來救我。”來喜把屋門治開，進去解了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石生。回到草屋把包袱背在身上。領著石生到外邊一看，那房子后邊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，有一小牆與當街相靠。就把石生扶過牆去，他也隨后跳出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    是夜，月色光明，如同白晝。二人往前緊走。石生道：“倘或賊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人隨后趕來，這卻怎處？”來喜道：“大爺放心，小的新學成一個拳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>棒，就有三二十人，還不是小的的敵手。請問大爺，緣何來到這里？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”石生把他私訪的來由說了。來喜磕頭道：“大爺高發，小的那里知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道。小的自從宅內出來流落此處。以賣線為生，至今還未成家哩。今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日幸逢大爺，不知還肯收留小的否？”石生道：“你是我的故人，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>跟我去罷，不必在此住了。”又往前走，約有五更時分，已到江邊了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。月下看見江中一只漁船，船上站著一個漁翁。頭戴斗笠，身披茅蓑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，正在那里下網。聽得他口中唱道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    駕小艇兮，鼓檜槳。擊空明兮，溯流光。侶魚蝦兮，凌萬頃。念</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>故主兮，來一方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    來喜這邊叫道：“快撐船來。”那漁翁問道：“是做什么的？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來喜答道：“是過江的。”那漁翁把船搖到岸前，來喜向上一望，訝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“你莫不是趙哥嗎？”那漁翁看了一看，說道：“你莫不是來喜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>嗎？奇遇，奇遇。”又問道：“那一個是誰？”來喜道：“是咱家大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>爺，目下做這省的布政司了。出來私訪，誤投賊店，被我救出。同跑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>到這里來，你快接上船去。”那漁翁雙手把石生攙入艙中，來喜隨后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>跳上。漁翁跪下道：“趙才給老爺叩頭。”石生道：“你且起來，作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>速送我過江去，咱再說話。”趙才道：“老爺已經上船，料賊趕來也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>無妨了。”開船走不多時，見有三四十個人從后趕來。見船已到江心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，無可奈何而回。過得江來，石生問趙才道：“你在此打漁為生，成</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了家沒有？”趙才道：“小的一身一口還不能從容，那有余錢娶老婆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”石生道：“既是這樣，你也跟我去罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石生帶著趙才來喜走到一座山前，是個南往北來的總路口。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>見兩個少年婦人哭的甚是可憐。石生分付來喜道：“你去問他為何這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>等悲楚？”那婦人道：“俺家姓李，系邵州府人，頗有家私。于前月</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>間，忽有大盜入宅，將几個男人盡情殺害。拿了俺許多金銀，虜了俺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>妯娌兩個，來到此處。嫌俺帶腳，拋下俺走了。欲要鳴冤，不知官在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>何處？欲待回家，不知從那路走？只得在此哀告往來行人，能代俺報</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>此仇者情愿嫁他為妻。”石生叫來喜找小轎二乘，把兩個婦人帶回衙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    次日，石生把私訪的真信，稟報巡撫。巡撫統兵前去，把洞中的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>叛賊盡行剿沒。石生差役把賊店中一干人犯拿到。仔細審究，打劫李</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>姓一案，就是這人。俱各照律正法。石生分付二婦人道：“你大仇已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>報，送你回籍去罷。”那婦人道：“小婦人有誓在先，能代為報仇者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，情愿嫁他為妻。今既蒙大老爺天恩，情愿住在內宅，任憑大老爺賞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人罷。落入賊手，已經月余，有何顏面見人？”石生勸之再三，兩婦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人死不肯去。石生就把大的配了趙才，小的配了來喜。朝夕在宅內伺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>候。石生私訪已畢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知秋英在家如何？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第十六回  碧霞宮神女授兵符</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說石生的衙門后邊，是一處花園。園內有一白石碑，其光可鑒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。至夜半時分，中有人喊馬嘶甲兵響亮之聲，聽的甚真。相傳這碑是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>衙門中的鎮物。歷來官長俱莫敢動移。石生往外面私訪時，秋英在宅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>中無事，只身步入花園，來看這碑。到了跟前，忽見這碑變成一門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兩扇俱開，從里邊走出兩個女童，說道：“娘娘有旨，請石夫人里面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>相會。”秋英跟著女童進去。當中是一條磚砌的甬路，兩墀下俱是些</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>異樹奇花。走有箭許，是一座紫石橋。從橋上過去，又走了數十步，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是一座朱紅大門。門上懸著一匾，匾上寫著“碧霞宮”三字。才到門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>首，又出來了四個仙女。兩個執著寶幡，兩個執著提爐。說道：“娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>娘候夫人多時？特著奴等相迎。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    秋英隨著寶幡又進了兩三層門，才是一座大殿。殿當中蓮花座上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，坐著一位娘娘。下邊放著四個繡墩，排著兩行侍女。秋英進的殿來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，望上行禮。娘娘辭道：“夫人尊貴，小神怎敢當禮。”命二仙女急</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>忙扶起，讓在東邊頭一個繡墩上坐下。秋英道：“賤妾塵埃俗人，何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>煩聖母相詔。”娘娘答道：“石武曲不久即應大敵，軍旅未嫻，何以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>制勝？夫人聰明過人，特請來把軍中一切機務，說與你知。日后誓師</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>郊原，你兩人庶可共賦六月，以奏膚功。”叫仙女取出兵書三卷，付</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>與秋英。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    娘娘說道：“這書名為《行軍機要》首一卷是天時，第二卷是地</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>利，第三卷是人和。自古以來，兵家總不外此三者。”秋英問道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>天時怎樣？”娘娘道：“春夏秋冬，天時之總名。其間所逢的月，逢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日辰，俱為天時。時逢吉日則勝。如湯以辛卯而破昆吾。武以甲子而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>克商紂是也。”秋英又問：“怎謂地之利？”娘娘說道：“山川林薄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>俱是地利。凡扎營必相地高下平坡，方可以保無恙。若依山靠林，使</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>敵兵得所埋伏，則受害不小。此楚師背離，而舍所為，貽患晉候。此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>務擇平坦寬闊之處，左右前后，俱無遮擋。這才是安營的吉地。”秋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>英又問道：“何謂人和？”娘娘道：“人和者眾人結成一心也。凡行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>軍之首先□人心。人心齊則氣壯，氣壯則力勇。一鼓而前，誰能御之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。若人懷異心，子棄其父，弟棄其兄，各鳥獸散，安能破敵。如殷旅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>之前途倒戈，這就是人不和的一個榜樣。”秋英道：“這三件是行軍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>大要，幸承聖母指明。但擺陣之法，終屬茫然，還求聖母詳說一番方</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>妙。”娘娘道：“這口說不如眼見，你隨我來。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    娘娘下了蓮坐。秋英隨后跟著。一曲一灣，走到一個演武廳前，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>娘娘上去坐定，秋英旁邊相陪。娘娘分付仙女道：“取我的兵符來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>”這個仙女轉入后廳，取出一杆紅旗遞給娘娘。娘娘接在手中，把紅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>旗一展。忽聽一陣風響，立時就有數萬人馬，站在演武廳前。娘娘分</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>付道：“今日操演，爾等有失律者，定行梟首。”眾兵丁無不唱喏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>娘娘把紅旗向東一擺，就成了一個陣勢。娘娘向秋英道：“這叫做八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>卦連環陣，生傷休死諸門俱備。昔年諸葛亮坐困陸郎，其遺跡至今尚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>在。此陣法之神妙莫測者也。”娘娘領著秋英下了將台，從生門而入</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，八門游遍。那吉那凶，說得清清楚楚。然即轉回廳台，從新坐下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>把紅旗向西一擺，又成了一個陣勢。秋英問道：“這是何陣？”娘娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“這名為一字長蛇陣，擊首則尾應，擊尾則首應，擊中則首尾俱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>應。此陣法之最活者也。”又把紅旗一擺，成了一個陣勢。對秋英道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“是為鵝陣。”又擺成一陣道：“是為鸛陣。”又把紅旗左邊一擺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，右邊一擺，眾兵丁交互奔騰，多時方住，成了一個陣勢，前后人馬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>相接，密如魚鱗。秋英問道：“這陣叫做什么？”娘娘道：“這陣名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>為魚鹿。昔年鄭庄公與周王戰于☆砥A用的就是這個陣法。”陣已擺</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>完，娘娘把紅旗一卷，數萬人馬，風流云散，當時就沒有了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    秋英謝道：“重煩娘娘指教，賤妾頓開茅塞。”娘娘道：“這系</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>你我有緣，方能遇的這般湊巧。”娘娘領著秋英，下了廳台。轉回殿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>內，仍照前坐定。娘娘分付仙女道：“取我兵符一道，付與石夫人帶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>去。”仙女取一紅旗交與秋英。娘娘道：“你后日臨陣時，把這兵符</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>執在手里，任所指麾，無不如意。成功以后，仍把這書與兵符交還于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>我。”秋英問道：“賤妾從何處給娘娘送來？”娘娘道：“這卻不勞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>你送，就把這書符供在香案桌上，默祝一番，我自有人來取。”秋英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>又為致謝。娘娘道：“我還有律詩一首贈你。你朝夕度念，方知軍務</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>艱難，不至于輕忽僨事。”遂手寫一詩道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    丈人行陣林師貞，何得輕心漫談兵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    無備終招懸雷奪，曳柴曾致班馬聲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    舟中掬指因爭濟，棄甲復來為食羹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    臨戎常懷量敵意，詰朝奏凱在盛京。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    娘娘把詩付與秋英道：“你回去再留心細看兵書，就成女中一員</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>名將。但系天機不可泄漏。”秋英應過。遂著兩個仙女，領著秋英從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>舊路送出。出的門時，秋英回頭一看，仍然是統石碑。秋英轉入內宅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，進了自己房中，把兵法神書秘秘收好，總不肯告訴別人。秋英自得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了這神書，白日不敢明看，俱是晚間，夜靜無人時，方才展開細玩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>從頭看去，并無一字半句，心中模糊。看至月余，行軍擺陣之法，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>遂一遭通了。心中暗忖道：“老爺是個文官，那至于身歷行伍。我乃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>女流，怎至于同赴疆場。聖母所囑，有些令人可疑。”這且不表。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石生，自從訪真了洞中的叛賊，巡撫喜其有功，奏知皇上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>皇上旨下，著浙江布政兼理按察事務。石茂蘭赴京引見。石生把一切</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>事務，交與委圖的官員。從河路往北而下。船至濟寧，有他一個同年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，姓殷名莫磐，字永安。聞石生路過本州，就上船來參拜。石生也下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>船去拜他。殷莫磐向石生道：“小弟選期已到，意欲赴京。苦無腳力</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，年兄大人，若肯攜帶前去，承情不淺。”石生答道：“這是弟所情</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>愿，明日請上船來同行。”到得次日，殷生收拾行李，上了船，與石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生同往京去。到了京中，石生引見聖上。聖上甚是嘉獎，著仍回原任</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>理事。殷生掣簽，選了廣東惠州府的同知。對石生道：“弟實望選在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>浙江，今天各一方，終不能蒙年兄的覆庇了。”石生道：“仕路窄狹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，安知不還遇在一處。”住了几日，石生辭殷生道：“年兄在京還有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>些事，故小弟實不能奉陪，不日就要先回浙江去了。”殷生道：“年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兄責任重大，小弟怎敢攀取。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生上了一疏，乞告假一，往羅田縣去祭祖。聖上批准。石生謝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過了恩，星夜往羅田縣而來。到了羅田郊界，那羅田縣的知縣卻迎二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>十余里，鋪設公館，饋送下程。石生概不敢當，在一客店內住下。石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生祭祖已過，仍回店中。辭別了縣主，一早起身而走。縣主又送了二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>十多里，方才回衙。石生從羅田縣，往赴浙水。剛才走了兩程，又下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了一道旨意：“浙江布政石茂蘭訪查有功，准升廣東巡撫。”石生接</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了旨意，務要往那衙門，再赴廣東上任。殷莫磐聞得此信，不勝忻喜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說秋英與翠容、春芳三個，無事閑談。管宅門的進來稟道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>大老爺高升廣東巡撫，紅報已到，小的先給太太叩喜。”秋英聽說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>諤然道：“廣東與苗民相近，老爺升到那里，戰伐之事終不免了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>就把兵書，逐夜留心細看，以預作准備。住不几日，石生回到衙門，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>把布按兩司的事務，一一交貸清楚。就擇日起身，率領家眷，來到廣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>東上任。一日殷莫磐特來參見，石生請至書房。殷生要行堂參禮，石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生斷斷不肯，仍分賓主而坐。殷生道：“卑職得到大人屬下，可謂天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>遂人愿了。”石生答道：“你我同榜，兄弟私交也。服勞王家公義也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。不忍以公而忘私，又安敢以私而廢公耶。”殷生聞言，凜然而退。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>回到衙門，小心辦事。并不敢少涉棄謁。住有半年，又提升他潮州府</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的知府。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知石生在廣東如何？再看下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第十七回  忘夙仇孤嫠脫困厄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說石生自浙江布政轉升了廣東巡撫。才到任時，進士王曰灼，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>親來看望。春芳向王進士道：“我房里缺人使喚，煩哥哥代我買一個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>送來。”王曰灼應允而去。回到家里，著媒婆尋找不題。卻說王詮之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>妻念氏，原系廣州府人。他父親念照遠，貿易黃州，因與王家結親。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>為自王詮死后，他兩個兄弟俱不成人，吃賭嫖三字全占。五六年間，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>把家產化了個盡絕。念照遠見他女兒既無子嗣，又無養膳，仍舊帶回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>廣州去了。那料念氏福薄，回到娘家沒過三年，父母雙亡。一切家資</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>被他兄弟念小三輸淨，落的在館驛里存身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    剩下念氏仍如無根的飄蓬一般。鄰里親戚愿其改適，他卻顧惜大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>體，執意不肯。屢次托媒婆說情，愿賣身為奴。媒婆聽得王進士買人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的風信，來向念氏說道：“你逐日叫俺給你找主，目下撫院大老爺衙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>內買人服事。三太太你可愿意去嗎？”念氏道：“怎么不愿意，但憑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>大嫂作成。我自有用錢謝你。”媒人貪圖用錢，領著念氏到了王進士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家，叫他先看一看。王進士見人甚利便，向媒婆道：“這人卻也去的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，問他要多少賣價。”念氏對媒人道：“要銀六十兩。”王進士道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“這卻也不多，但寫文約誰人作主？”媒婆道：“他是沒丈夫的，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>無父母。叫他兄弟念小三來罷。”王進士道：“石太太用人甚急，既</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是情愿，就要當日成交。”媒婆著人到館驛叫了念小三來。說道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>你姐姐賣身賣妥了，同著你寫張文約，還有二兩銀子給你。”念小三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>正缺錢使，聽說這話，喜不自勝。就慨然同著寫了一張文約，得銀二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>兩走了。把媒人錢打發清楚，就住在王進士宅內。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了次日，念氏打整打整身面，王進士雇小轎一乘，著人抬送撫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>院衙門里去。念氏進的宅來，從上而下磕頭已畢。就在春芳房里，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>離左右，一切應承，無不小心。一日春芳向秋英道：“姐姐你看新來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的這個媽媽好像個鄉紳人家的派頭。在此作奴，我甚是不安。”秋英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“你何不問他個詳細。”春芳就把念氏叫到秋英房里來。念氏問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“太太有何使喚？”秋英道：“別無話說，你進宅已經數日，你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的來歷，俺還未問你個清白。看你的舉止動靜，與俺們不相上下。你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>實說你是什么人家，為何落得這般。”念氏哭著答道：“既到了這個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>地位，說也是多了。”秋英道：“你不妨實說。”念氏道：“家丑不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>可外言，說了恐太太們笑話。”秋英道：“萬屬得已誰肯賣身，你實</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>說你是那里人？”念氏稟道：“小婦人是黃州府羅田縣永寧街上王家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的媳婦。公公王有章是個兩榜，曾做過京宦。丈夫王詮是個文生與對</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>門石知府的公子石生為友。見石生之妻房氏顏氏絕世，心起不良。逐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>日謀算，后值石生修河在外，千方百計，竟把房氏娶到家來。是夜王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>詮死倒在地，房氏并不知那里去了。小婦人有兩個小叔，從他哥死以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>后，把家產化訖。落的小婦人并無依靠。不料回到娘家，又父母雙亡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。止有一個兄弟，又把家產輸盡，目下落的在館驛里住。小婦人無可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>奈何，只得賣身宅內，以終余年。萬望老爺太太垂憐則個。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    秋英把念氏的一段言語，盡告訴了翠容。翠容大怒道：“這是我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的冤家對頭到了，我一定報報前仇。”秋英道：“姐姐差了，那是他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>男人做的事，與他何涉。這人現今落在咱家，即以你我為主，正該逐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>事行些方便。如何反提前仇，徒落得自己度量窄小。”翠容悟道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>妹子說的極是。再告訴老爺看他怎樣？”正說間，石生闖到屋里，問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>道：“你兩個方才說的什么？”秋英答道：“說的是三太太房里那個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>媽媽。”石生道：“有甚說頭？”翠容道：“他不是別人，就是你的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>好朋友王詮的老婆。落得這般了。”石生道：“真是他嗎？”秋英道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“真正是他。”石生向翠容道：“據王詮所為，就把這個婦人處死</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，尚未足泄夫人之恨。但王詮所為，未必是這個婦人的主意。身死家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>敗，妻落人手，如此報應，已覺難堪了。刻薄之事，切不可做。況我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>當急難時，他曾助銀五百，其情未為不厚。至今尚未還他。追想昔日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的交情，則他婦人在此為奴，終覺過意不去。二位夫人看該何以相處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>？”秋英答道：“以妾看來死后無仇，這個婦人老爺應該周恤他才是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。昔日他曾助銀五百，今日就該照數還他，以償前債。外再助銀若干</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，以盡友情。問他若愿意回籍，差人送去。如此做來，就令王詮有靈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>應，亦感愧于地下矣。”石生道：“二夫人言之有理，下官就依這樣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>做罷。”這正是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    識起一切俗情外，發言盡歸款要中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了次日，石生同著三位夫人，把念氏叫到跟前。說道：“夜日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>聽見太太們說，你是王詮的室人。王詮與本院素系朋友，你可知道嗎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>？”念氏答道：“小婦人不知。”石生道：“本院就是你對門住的石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>茂蘭。”念氏聽說，跪倒在地磕頭，央道：“亡夫所為，罪該萬死。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>小婦人但憑太太、老爺盡情發放罷。”石生笑道：“娘子請起，本院</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>并無別意。”那念氏那里敢動。三位夫人過去親手拉起來。石生說道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“從前的事再不提了。本院念故人情腸，意欲周濟你還家。或廣州</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>或羅田，任從你便。”念氏道：“大人額外施恩，小女人沒世不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>但廣州娘家無人，仍回羅田去罷。”石生道：“你既愿回羅田，少住</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>些時，本院就著人送你去。”自此以后，三位夫人，俱以客禮待念氏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。并不叫他在房里伺候了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生衙內，有個長隨，名叫張忠。是羅田縣人。甚是老成得托。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>石生就叫他去送念氏回家。還叫他路過襄陽，稟問胡員外的近安。字</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>請朱良玉、蔡敬符同來衙門照料些事務。宅內設席給念氏餞行。石生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>叫秋英封銀子五百兩整，交與念氏。石生道：“王兄在日，曾助我銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子五百，這五百兩銀子是還前賬的。”外又封銀子三百兩，說道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>這三百銀子，是本院分外相幫的。有這八百銀子，老嫂盡可坐終余年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了。”念氏謝道：“照數還債，已覺討愧。分外相幫，賤妾如何敢當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”三位夫人，又各贈銀子二十兩，以作路費。念氏起身，三位夫人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>親送出宅門，方才回去。時人有詩，贊石生道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    夙怨不藏世所鮮，包荒大度肖坤乾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    幫金克仿贈袍意，遙送几同棧道前。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    格外施恩全友道，幽魂負慚在九泉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    莫云偶爾恤孤寡，正為后昆造福田。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說張忠帶著几封家書，同著一個老媽，扶事念氏，扑了正路。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>當起旱處起旱，當坐船處坐船。不多些時，來到襄陽。張忠下船，各</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>處投字去了。念氏在船上偶一合眼，看見丈夫王詮走入艙中。說道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“賢妻你回來了？我生前做的何事，石大人卻不記念夙仇。還周濟你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>回家，真使我愧悔無及了。但當異日相報罷。”念氏醒來，心中怨恨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>王詮，感激石郎。反來復去，甚是不快。適張忠已經回到船來，走的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>與羅田相近。那張忠雇了轎子，把念氏送還王宅。他兩個小叔，見念</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>氏回來。愁無養膳，意味作難。念氏道：“叔叔不必這樣，我自有銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>子養生。”兩個小叔驚問道：“嫂嫂的銀子，從何處得來？莫不是娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家給你的嗎？”念氏道：“非也。”兩個小叔道：“既不是娘家給你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的，是那里來的銀子？”念氏就把自己賣身，并石生還債幫金之事，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一一說了。兩個小叔感泣道：“石大人何盛德若斯也！吾兄生平所為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，叫弟等代為慚恧無地矣。”兩個兄弟得了他嫂子這宗銀子，努力持</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>家。數年以后，家產恢復。子弟亦有入泮發身者。皆石生相激之力也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。此是后話，無庸多說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說張忠從黃州復歸襄陽。請了朱舉人、蔡副榜同來到衙門。石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生請入內書房相會，敘禮已畢。蔡副榜進內宅看過了秋英。朱舉人看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過了春芳。出來坐下。蔡副榜道：“妹丈大人，吉人天相，近來的福</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>氣，倍勝從前了。”朱舉人道：“惠風善政，一入境來，如雷轟耳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>弟亦多為叨光了。”石生答道：“小弟材不勝任，全賴二兄相幫。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是夕閑談之間，說及送念氏回籍一事。朱舉人、蔡副榜俱稱贊道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>如此舉行，方見大人的度量。”石生又差人往廣州，請了王進士，來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>到衙門中一會。彼此相見，自不覺暢懷。這蔡副榜合朱舉人，石生俱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>留在衙中，照料些事務。王進士在衙中，住了月余，仍回廣州去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    但不知石生后來官到何處？要知端的，聽下回分解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第十八回  建奇功全家受榮華</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說石生在廣州做巡撫。忽有邊吏來報說：苗寇大發，搶奪人家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>的錢財，虜掠人家的妻女。聲勢甚是洶勇。石生不敢隱匿，據實奏知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>皇上。皇上旨下：特加石茂蘭兵部尚書銜，令挂帥印前去平定。石生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>接旨已過，退入內宅。向秋英夫人道：“下官只通文墨，那曉得軍旅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。一旦身任元戎，何以克稱厥職。煩夫人代為平才，下官好再作道理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”秋英答道：“朝廷旨無容抗違，臣子職分理應御侮。老爺一去，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>開國承家，端在此舉。安可以英雄態故作懦夫狀。戰陣之事，賤妾頗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>悉大略。若不棄嫌，情愿親操旗鼓，隨營辦事。”石生大喜道：“夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人既有這番韜略，下官才覺放心。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    次日，就在演武廳操兵。以秋英為先鋒，以左右二營為兩隊。殷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>莫磐情愿軍前效力，就以他為監軍。率領馬步兵丁兩萬余人，分下已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>定。正是人馬強壯，器械鮮明，直往邊庭進發。一路行來，俱是秋英</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>究九了地勢，然后扎營。來得與苗寇相近，擇了一個高埠去處，安下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了營盤。秋英向石生道：“苗寇依山靠海，出沒無常。今日大軍初到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000001999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，人困馬乏。苗寇以逸待勞，夜間必來劫寨。當預作准備。”石生道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>：“號令全憑出自夫人，下官坐鎮中間而已。”秋英就把兩隊人馬分</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>為四路埋伏。去大營不過二三里許。寨中只留三二十人藏在一邊，候</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>劫寨的風信。苗寇來到營中，見是個空寨，必然搶奪東西。就以放炮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>為號，四面殺來，必獲大勝。分付停當。寨旁有一座小山，秋英同石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>生躲在山上，遠遠料望。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    是夜，苗寇見官兵扎下營寨。商議道：“官兵方從遠來，必然疲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>倦。今夜乘黑劫寨，是為上策。”其中有一個頭目，叫做賽天王。領</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>了兩千人馬，暗地闖入官兵寨中。四下一看，并無兵馬。只剩得許多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>器械，就下得馬來。這個搶衣甲，那個搶弓箭，你東我西。賽天王也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>約束不住了。寨中的伏兵見其人亂，放了一聲號炮。四面伏兵一齊殺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>來。苗寇知是中計，出寨急走。早被官兵緊緊圍住。左右沖突，再不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>能出去了。殺到天明，苗寇只落得一二十人，乘間竊逃而去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    秋英石生下山回寨。宰牛殺羊，犒勞軍士不題。石生向秋英道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“今日之功，建自夫人運籌決勝。苗寇平定應無難矣。”秋英答道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“老爺休要矜張。疆場之事，一彼一此，勢不兩立。苗雖小蠢，斷難</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>長甘退舍。”石生閉口無言。卻說賽天王領著一二十名敗卒，奔回本</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>寨。稟知寨主哪思哩說：“官兵神妙不測，難以爭勝。”哪思哩道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>“我只說石巡撫是個白面書生，不諳軍務。那料想被他殺的這般盡絕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，此仇不報，何以雄據一方，圖謀中原呢？”又差人來下戰書，石生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>批道：“約于來月十六日會戰。”秋英向石生道：“苗寇再來，必然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>統領大眾，以圖報仇。”少有疏忽，爾我恐為所虜。”石生道：“這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>當怎處？”秋英道：“老爺放心，賤妾自有運用。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    到得那月十六日，黎明時分。秋英著守營寨造一樓車：高三丈有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>余，坐在上面以便望敵。石生領著左右兩隊大軍，一鼓而出。走了不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>過十里，望見敵壘了。又向前走了三五里路，已與苗寇對鋒。從那陣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>前閃出一位苗王，身披鎧甲，手執鐵矛。厲聲問道：“來將何名？敢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>侵犯吾境？”石生答道：“吾乃巡撫石茂蘭。奉命討賊，速速下馬投</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>降，免你一死。”苗王大怒罵道：“好死囚，你前日折損我許多的人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>馬，今日又在陣前夸口。看我拿你下馬，以報前仇。”摧馬挺矛，直</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>取石生。石生終是個文字官，不會廝殺。見苗寇上來的凶猛，料敵他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>不過。撥馬便走，跑不半里，就跌落馬下。苗王急忙使矛刺來。忽見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一人，把石生背在身上，騰空而去。苗寇一直追趕。秋英在樓車上遙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>望，敗卒將近。把兵符一擺，陡起了一陣黑風，對面看不見人。那苗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>寇撤身轉回。這邊金鼓齊鳴。苗寇正摸路時，自相殘殺，早已血流滿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>地，尸橫遍野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    苗王哪思哩回到寨中，與眾首領商議道：“石督府營內，定有異</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>人。不可以智力相角。莫若暫且投降為妙。眾人俱不愿意。卻說石生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>被那個人背到寨后，把石生放在地下。說道：“大人已脫敵難，請緩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>步回寨去罷。”石生問道：“你是何人？幸蒙相救。”那人答道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>我乃王詮，蒙大人不念舊惡，周濟念氏回籍。無可圖報，故特來一救</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>，聊當結草。”說罷，再看不見人了。石生回寨，暫且不提。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說哪思哩與眾人計議道：“石鏡山朝陽洞，有一個百花公主，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>法能剪紙成兵。請他來相助一陣，或者能制伏官兵，也未可知。遂立</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>時著人持書去請。那公主拆書一看，慨然應許。率領一萬人馬而來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>與苗寇合為大營。又來搦戰。秋英向石生道：“出陣不用旁人，待賤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>妾與殷莫磐，俺兩個出去收功罷。”秋英戎裝當先，殷莫磐隨后。只</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>領五六千人馬，徑赴陣前。那邊百花公主當頭，哪思哩殿后。統領數</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>萬銳卒，從南殺來。望見官兵寡少，就四下里團團圍住。秋英用護罩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>法把自家的兵馬護定，任他左攻右擊，總不能傷損一個。只見苗陣內</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有人背一箱子，周遭跑走。那兵馬越殺越多，不計其數。秋英窺透其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>朮，把兵符向上一擺，忽然一聲霹靂，雨如盆傾。那苗兵漸漸減去，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>落地的多是紙人紙馬，被雨一淋，就不能動移了。秋英把兵符又往下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>一擺，這邊的兵馬漸覺眾多。殺了半個時辰，就有十萬天兵，把百花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>公主、哪里哩兩路人馬殺的几乎片甲不回。百花公主領著殘兵仍歸本</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>洞。哪思哩回寨，瞞怨道：“我要投降，你們不肯。又惹了一場大辱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。”有眾頭目，莫敢發言。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    再說秋英回的寨來，殷莫磐問道：“此陣雖獲大勝，倘苗寇再來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>為之奈何？”秋英答道：“這一陣苗寇俱膽戰心驚，不久即來投降了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。何煩再動干戈。”果然，次日苗王遣人賚降表來投降。其表曰：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    伏惟：聖德同天，無遠弗屆。異域無識，狡思啟疆。茲經大兵所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>剿，始信王化難越。嗣后愿備遠服，共沐皇風。如違納貢之常，甘受</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>后至之戮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生據其降表，奏聞朝廷。聖上准其投降。石生又極力勸化了一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>番，方才班師。苗王親送石生百有余里，然后歸寨。這正是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    奏捷馬敲金鐙響，破敵人唱凱歌還。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生作詩一首，贊秋英道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    兵家豈第論虛孤，帷幄運籌防不虞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    娘子稱軍惟唐主，婦人夸戎成伯圖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    只知男輩多雄略，那料女流有武夫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    簪珥暫當甲冑用，旌旗指處瞻城烏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說秋英與石生回了衙門，著人擺上香案默祝，聖母把神書兵符</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>俱各收去。聖上因石生有功，特升兵部尚書，協同內閣辦事。誥封秋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>英為菄Z夫人。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    奉天承運皇帝詔曰：治道立昌文德，不廢夫武功。勛猷大就，男</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>謀必需乎女助。爾蔡氏乃浙江布政使司石茂蘭之側室，夙樹芳型，尤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>多雄略。務效忠于王家，不憚親操旗鼓。思克相于夫子，罔恤身歷疆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>場。茲爾平苗有功，誥封爾為菄Z夫人。于戲，紫泥煥彩，用標一時</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>之榮。彤管流輝，永垂不朽之譽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生赴京上任，謝恩已畢。又請了兩付冠誥，封贈翠容春芳。住</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>有半年，秋英向石生道：“人生世上，富貴尚至卿相尊榮極矣。有遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>慮者，必須急流勇退，方可善全始終。不然樹大招風，恐無日不在搖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>動中也。”石生道：“夫人所見極高，下官不久即當告退。”是歲正</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><h5>該會試，石生又主一次大場，收了許多門生。程誘蝯{輓鱄悁C門下</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。大場已過，遂因腳病，不便動轉。告老致仕而還，仍歸襄陽居住。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    石生思念，發跡雖在襄陽，羅田終系故土。先人墳墓所在，祭掃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>如何便宜。后翠容生二子，聘胡員外兩位孫女。秋英生一子，聘朱良</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>玉之女為妻。春芳生一子，聘蔡敬符之女為妻。石生領著翠容母子仍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>回羅田。秋英春芳母子，俱住在襄陽。石生一年襄陽，一年羅田，兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>下往來，甚是如意。嗣后石生四子，俱經高發。朱舉人□了詞林，蔡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>敬符中了正科。殷莫磐以隨營有功，做了兵備守道。王曰灼做了知府</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。石生晚年康健，直活到年近百余，方損館舍。退升這日，天鼓齊鳴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>。奉旨謚為“武勇公”崇祀□□。翠容二子，一支承祧本宗，一個過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>繼房門。至今石生之后，一支黃州，兩支襄陽。石氏后裔，因其先人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>皆蒙鬼神護佑。買了一處大宅子，就中蓋一寺院。前殿是佛祖，中殿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>是觀音，后殿是太白金星。招募僧道，治買祭田。俎豆馨香，四時不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>絕。石氏人口蕃盛，登嵬科，做顯宦者代不乏人。因石生功德之所積</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>也。亦何非鬼神之默助乎。后人有詩總斷道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e01a8927891ede54/text/000002097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e01a8927891ede54-f09fcd twpub-e01a8927891ede54-6b4cd0\"><p>    二氣彌綸布太空，何論南朔與西東。</p></div>"
